me%20the%20first%20train%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20to%20be%20hitched%20with%20the%20double-decker%20coaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEnd%20of%20an%20era!%20The%20last%20public%20service%20of%20non-AC%20double%20decker%20coaches%20of%20the%20iconic%20Flying%20Ranee%20Express%20train%20entered%20Mumbai%20Central%20station%20this%20morning.%20From%20this%20evening%2C%20the%20train%20has%20been%20upgraded%20with%20LHB-class%20upgraded%20version%20of%20coaches%2C%20but%20is%20sadly%20not%20a%20double%20decker%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rajendra%20Aklekar%2C%20journalist%20and%20author%20on%20India's%20rail%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCould%20not%20miss%20the%20historic%20last%20run%20of%20the%20double%20decker%20coaches%20for%20anything.%20They%20were%20introduced%20on%20the%20train%20exactly%2043%20years%20six%20months%2029%20days%20ago.%20The%20only%20double%20decker%20train%20to%20remain%20now%20is%20the%20Valsad%20Fast%20Passenger%2C%20operated%20by%20Western%20Railway%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Aklekar%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689534600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fu2ocv9k_flying-ranee-train_625x300_17_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflying-ranee-train-loses-iconic-double-decker-coaches-after-4-decades-4213193%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Railways%20and%20Textiles%20Darshana%20Jardosh%20flagged%20off%20the%20train%20and%20also%20travelled%20over%20200%20km%20on%20the%20train%20from%20Mumbai%20Central%20to%20Surat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflying-ranee-train-loses-iconic-double-decker-coaches-after-4-decades-4213193%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflying-ranee-train-loses-iconic-double-decker-coaches-after-4-decades-4213193%2Famp%2F1