device%20that's%20capable%20of%20rolling%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimage-ppubs.uspto.gov%2Fdirsearch-public%2Fprint%2FdownloadPdf%2F20230221766%5C%22%3Epatent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20filed%20in%20November%20and%20published%20on%20July%2013%2C%20demonstrates%20a%20design%20for%20a%20rolling%20phone%20that%20relies%20on%20thinned%20glass%20and%20components%20that%20place%20compressive%20pressure%20on%20the%20screen%20to%20ensure%20the%20display%20is%20not%20damaged%20when%20rolled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20patent%20is%20for%20general%20electronic%20displays%2C%20Apple%20specifically%20noted%20in%20the%20application%20this%20design%20could%20be%20used%20for%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20would%20be%20joining%20Samsung%2C%20Motorola%2C%20and%20LG%20in%20the%20quest%20to%20bring%20to%20market%20a%20rollable%20smartphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Samsung%20and%20Motorola%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnet.com%2Ftech%2Fmobile%2Fwhy-you-wont-be-buying-a-rollable-phone-anytime-soon%2F%5C%22%3Ealso%20working%20toward%20a%20rollable%20phone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20neither%20company%20has%20actually%20brought%20the%20product%20to%20market.%20LG%20too%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flg-rollable-phone-screen-expands-video-ces-2021-2021-1%5C%22%3Eadvertised%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20rollable%20phone%20that%20they%20have%20yet%20to%20release.%20The%20company%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D52f11b749a32c4b60a50256f08f69d25aa21b42b24b99ab03bc4cd1e0c3ed2fd%26postID%3D64b41a0122f2a9342c4220b6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.lg.com%252Fglobal%252Flg-signature%252Frollable-oled-tv-r%5C%22%3Esells%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20rollable%20OLED%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-iphone-may-roll-into-a-cylinder-apple-patent-suggests-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689529787000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b4266764dab3001999e1ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-iphone-may-roll-into-a-cylinder-apple-patent-suggests-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20appears%20to%20be%20joining%20Samsung%2C%20Motorola%2C%20and%20LG%20in%20the%20quest%20to%20bring%20to%20market%20a%20rollable%20smartphone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Hawkinson%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-iphone-may-roll-into-a-cylinder-apple-patent-suggests-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Inheritance%20Of%20Uncertainty%3A%20What's%20In%20Store%20For%20Property%20In%20Civil%20Code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20about%20three%20weeks%20now%2C%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20has%20ignited%20a%20debate%20around%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20country%20that%20exists%20not%20just%20among%20its%20people%20but%20also%20in%20its%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Commission%20on%20Friday%20extended%20the%20deadline%20for%20public%20submissions%20on%20the%20UCC%20till%20July%2028%20due%20to%20an%20overwhelming%20response.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20commission%20has%20received%20over%2027%20lakh%20replies%20through%20emails%2C%20and%20the%20commission%20is%20likely%20to%20begin%20nation-wide%20public%20consultations%20and%20share%20a%20detailed%20questionnaire%20with%20citizens%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInheritance%2C%20adoption%2C%20marriage%20and%20divorce%20have%20been%20largely%20governed%20by%20personal%20laws%20in%20the%20country.%20Even%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20treading%20carefully%20on%20UCC.%20They%20have%20not%20opposed%20reforms%20in%20personal%20laws%20such%20as%20equality%20of%20inheritance%2C%20but%20held%20that%20a%20UCC%20can%20be%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20cultural%20identity%20of%20Muslims%20and%20diversity%20in%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInheritance%20has%20been%20a%20sticking%20point%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20uniformity%2C%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20women%20regarding%20inheritance%20have%20differed%20based%20on%20religion%20in%20India.%20Inheritance%20or%20succession%20is%20anyway%20an%20emotive%20matter%20in%20Indian%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22vlm8ecjo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2Fvlm8ecjo_india-crowd-generic_625x300_18_June_19.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20religion%20follows%20its%20own%20personal%20law%20for%20property%20devolution.%20Not%20only%20different%20religious%20groups%2C%20but%20even%20subgroups%20have%20their%20own%20local%20customs%20and%20norms%20with%20their%20property%20rights.%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%20and%20Jain%20follow%20a%20code%20of%20property%20codified%20under%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%2C%201956%2C%20while%20Christians%20follow%20another%20code%20and%20Muslims%20have%20not%20codified%20their%20property%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%2C%201956%2C%20Hindu%20women%20have%20equal%20rights%20to%20inherit%20property%20from%20their%20parents%20and%20have%20the%20same%20entitlement%20as%20Hindu%20men.%20But%20implementation%20differs%2C%20specifically%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20agricultural%20land%2C%20and%20while%20courts%20have%20also%20intervened%20many%20times%20to%20implement%20equal%20share%20for%20women%20in%20parental%20property%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20has%20to%20do%20with%20societal%20norms%20that%20lead%20to%20many%20women%20not%20even%20claiming%20their%20property%20rights%2C%20say%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20women%2C%20governed%20by%20the%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%2C%20are%20entitled%20to%20a%20share%20of%20their%20husband's%20property%20depending%20on%20the%20presence%20of%20children%2C%20but%20daughters%20get%20a%20share%20less%20than%20sons.%20Now%2C%20the%20UCC%20aims%20to%20enforce%20a%20uniform%20legal%20framework%20in%20respect%20of%20all%20such%20facets%2C%20for%20all%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayank%20Mohanka%2C%20taxation%20expert%20and%20founder-director%20at%20taxaaram.com%2C%20told%20NDTV%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20for%20framers%20of%20the%20UCC%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20inheritance%20will%20be%20the%20framing%20of%20a%20unified%20code%20for%20such%20diverse%20and%20varied%20laws%20of%20inheritance%2C%20which%20also%20imbibes%20within%20itself%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20respective%20personal%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22india%20crowd%20generic%20istock%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-08%2Findia-crowd-generic-istock_650x400_61503730268.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%2C%20he%20said%2C%20if%20a%20man%20leaves%20behind%20property%2C%20it%20is%20primarily%20passed%20on%20to%20his%20%26quot%3BClass%20I%26quot%3B%20heirs%20(the%20widow%2C%20children%20and%20mother)%20in%20equal%20share.%20In%20their%20absence%2C%20%26quot%3BClass%20II%26quot%3B%20heirs%20(father%2C%20grandchildren%2C%20great-grandchildren%2C%20brother%2C%20sister%20and%20other%20relatives)%20can%20claim%20the%20property.%20But%20the%20rules%20change%20when%20the%20owner%20is%20a%20Hindu%20woman%20and%20when%20she%20dies%20without%20a%20will%2C%20the%20assets%20get%20passed%20on%20to%20her%20husband%20and%20children%20in%20equal%20proportion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20none%20of%20them%20are%20present%2C%20the%20property%20will%20go%20to%20the%20heirs%20of%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20it%20is%20only%20after%20that%20it%20will%20go%20to%20her%20parents%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20panel%20in%20Uttarakhand%20that%20will%20submit%20its%20UCC%20draft%20to%20the%20government%20soon%20has%20said%20gender%20parity%20in%20all%20laws%2C%20including%20inheritance%2C%20is%20a%20top%20focus%20area.%20There%20are%20established%20propositions%20of%20inheritance%20that%20are%20governed%20by%20the%20personal%20laws%2C%20but%20they%20are%20contrary%20to%20Indian%20laws%2C%20so%20it%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20if%20the%20UCC%20will%20also%20lead%20to%20changes%20in%20income%2C%20and%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20emerging%20concern%20among%20stakeholders%20and%20experts%20is%20the%20legal%20status%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Undivided%20Family%20(HUF).%20The%20Income%20Tax%20Act%20gives%20a%20separate%20legal%20%26quot%3Bperson%26quot%3B%20status%20to%20an%20HUF%2C%20entitling%20it%20to%20many%20tax%20benefits%2C%20and%20also%20in%20home%20loans%20and%20medical%20insurance%20premiums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22ijvqmeuo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fijvqmeuo_india-generic_625x300_28_December_22.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%2C%20a%20HUF%20can%20run%20its%20own%20business%20to%20generate%20income%20and%20claim%20all%20applicable%20exemptions%20and%20deductions%20that%20an%20individual%20is%20entitled%20to.%20The%20idea%20behind%20the%20HUF%20was%20to%20promote%20the%20joint%20family's%20interest%20over%20the%20individual's%20interest%2C%20and%20the%20HUF%20has%20been%20in%20place%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%20if%20the%20UCC%20is%20implemented%2C%20would%20the%20separate%20%26quot%3Bperson%26quot%3B%20status%20of%20an%20HUF%20continue%3F%20How%20will%20it%20affect%20lakhs%20of%20HUFs%20currently%20filing%20their%20income%20tax%20returns%20and%20availing%20tax%20deductions%20and%20exemptions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Mohanka%2C%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20HUF%20has%20always%20been%20considered%20the%20basic%20yet%20effective%20tool%20of%20tax%20planning%20within%20the%20permissible%20limits%20of%20the%20income%20tax%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20can%20also%20affect%20inheritance%20in%20tribal%20communities.%20Many%20tribes%20have%20customary%20laws%20and%20practices%20of%20inheritance%20of%20property%2C%20sometimes%20going%20to%20the%20oldest%20son%2C%20and%20often%20going%20to%20the%20youngest%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanthal%20communities%2C%20and%20many%20tribes%20across%20Jharkhand%20and%20the%20northeast%20have%20openly%20issued%20statements%20saying%20the%20UCC%20can%20disrupt%20their%20society%20that%20has%20varied%20norms%20of%20inheritance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20voices%20in%20the%20government%2C%20including%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Health%20SP%20Baghel%2C%20have%20made%20it%20clear%20the%20UCC%20will%20not%20touch%20the%20rights%20of%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689529320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2Fk4f997ug_india-crowd-generic_625x300_24_December_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-inheritance-of-uncertainty-whats-in-store-for-property-in-civil-code-4213329%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20about%20three%20weeks%20now%2C%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20has%20ignited%20a%20debate%20around%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20country%20that%20exists%20not%20just%20among%20its%20people%20but%20also%20in%20its%20laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-inheritance-of-uncertainty-whats-in-store-for-property-in-civil-code-4213329%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-inheritance-of-uncertainty-whats-in-store-for-property-in-civil-code-4213329%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-inheritance-of-uncertainty-whats-in-store-for-property-in-civil-code-4213329%2Famp%2F1%22