Fa%3E%20more%20than%20four%20years%20after%20breaking%20ties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20formal%20announcement%20to%20ally%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20all%20speculation%20about%20his%20future%20alignment.%20For%20months%20he%20had%20been%20inching%20closer%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%20after%20breaking%20up%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20last%20year%20following%20an%20unsuccessful%20attempt%20at%20dethroning%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbhar%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20not%20only%20proves%20his%20importance%20in%20the%20caste%20jigsaw%20of%20the%20state%20but%20also%20provides%20a%20definite%20fillip%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%20eastern%20UP%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20It%20is%20a%20demoralising%20event%20for%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205326%2FF1IS5bJaAAATffk.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205326%2FF1IS5bJaAAATffk.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205326%2FF1IS5bJaAAATffk-300x218.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205326%2FF1IS5bJaAAATffk-1024x743.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663497%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22871%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOm%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40oprajbhar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20still%20a%20marginal%20player%20in%20the%20larger%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20Rajbhar%20has%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20emerged%20as%20a%20vocal%20and%20visible%20factor%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E-oriented%20(caste)%20struggle%20for%20representation%20within%20the%20OBCs%20in%20Eastern%20UP.%20His%20topsy-turvy%20career%20trajectory%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20also%20helps%20us%20trace%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20politics%20of%20%E2%80%98social%20justice%E2%80%99%20of%20marginalised%20backward%20castes%20over%20the%20last%20three%20decades%E2%80%94from%20Kanshiram%20to%20Modi.%20These%20dynamics%20have%20become%20more%20pronounced%20under%20the%20rise%20and%20rule%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20cunningly%20merged%20Hindutva%20with%20caste-based%20mobilisation%20to%20outmuscle%20and%20outmanoeuvre%20its%20opponents%20in%20four%20consecutive%20elections%20since%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20announced%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20two%20days%20after%20they%20met%20for%20an%20hour%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20discuss%20the%20modalities%2C%20which%20have%20not%20been%20revealed%20as%20of%20now.%20Speculation%20is%20rife%20that%20Rajbhar%2C%20who%20contested%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20independently%20as%20a%20rebel%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20wants%20his%20party%20to%20contest%20some%20seats%20in%20the%20SBSP%E2%80%99s%20stronghold%20around%20Ghazipur-Mau.%20He%20could%20also%20return%20to%20the%20state%20cabinet%20led%20by%20Adityanath.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbhar%20is%20an%20MLA%20from%20Zahoorabad%20constituency%20in%20Ghazipur.%20In%202022%2C%20six%20candidates%20of%20the%20SBSP%2C%20including%20him%20and%20Abbas%20Ansari%2C%20the%20son%20of%20jailed%20former%20legislator%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%2C%20won%20their%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20Opposition%20alliance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20arrival%20of%20Rajbharji%2C%20the%20NDA%20will%20become%20stronger%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20NDA%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Modiji%20towards%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20deprived%20sections%20will%20gain%20strength%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20tweeted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20Rajbhar%20too%20announced%20that%20the%20SBSP%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20come%20together.%20The%20two%20parties%20will%20fight%20together%20for%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20justice%2C%20national%20security%2C%20good%20governance%20and%20to%20empower%20the%20deprived%2C%20oppressed%2C%20backward%20castes%2C%20Dalits%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%2C%20youth%20and%20all%20weaker%20sections%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajbhar.%20The%20word%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAlpsankhyak%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eor%20minority%20(a%20reference%20to%20Muslims)%20was%20conspicuous%20by%20its%20omission.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Lucknow%2C%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20a%20jubilant%20Rajbhar%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20main%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20for%20failing%20to%20stitch%20together%20an%20alliance.%20He%20criticised%20them%20for%20their%20inability%20to%20keep%20with%20them%20smaller%20caste-based%20parties.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20there%20is%20any%20contest%20left%20in%20UP%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajbhar%2C%20vowing%20to%20help%20the%20NDA%20win%20all%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbhar%E2%80%99s%20low-key%20return%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%2C%20through%20two%20tweets%20and%20a%20self-organised%20press%20conference%2C%20stands%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20huge%20show%20of%20strength%20he%20had%20put%20up%20to%20formalise%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%202016%20and%20then%20with%20the%20SP%20in%202021.%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20relevance%20in%20UP%20politics%20helps%20us%20trace%20the%20rise%20and%20downfall%20of%20the%20Kanshiram-model%20of%20social%20engineering%20and%20the%20compatibility%20of%20the%20backward%20caste%20politics%20with%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbhar%2C%20who%20has%20built%20his%20own%20constituency%20through%20a%20blunt%20and%20rustic%20demeanour%20distinctive%20of%20Purvanchal%2C%20was%20born%20to%20a%20Bhar%20(OBC)%20family%20in%20Varanasi%20in%201962.%20He%20tried%20his%20luck%20at%20farming%20and%20drove%20autos%20and%20jeeps%20for%20a%20living%20before%20joining%20politics%20with%20the%20movement%20led%20by%20Dalit-Bahujan%20ideologue%20Kanshiram%20who%20had%20formed%20the%20Dalit%20Shoshit%20Samaj%20Sangarsh%20Samiti%20or%20DS4%20in%201981.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20BSP%20came%20into%20being%20in%201984%2C%20Rajbhar%20rose%20to%20be%20its%20Varanasi%20district%20president%20in%201996%20when%20he%20also%20contested%20his%20first%20Assembly%20election%20on%20a%20BSP%20ticket%20from%20Kolasla%20seat.%20Rajbhar%20stood%20third%20but%20lost%20to%20the%20winner%20Ajay%20Rai%2C%20then%20BJP%20candidate%20and%20now%20an%20opponent%20of%20Modi%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20by%20less%20than%206%2C000%20votes%2C%20securing%20a%20decent%20tally%20of%2032%2C777%20votes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbhar%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20the%20BSP%2C%20however%2C%20soured%20after%20he%20developed%20differences%20with%20Mayawati%2C%20Kanshiram%E2%80%99s%20chosen%20mentee%20who%20would%20go%20on%20to%20succeed%20him%20as%20the%20supremo%20and%20also%20become%20chief%20minister.%20He%20accused%20Mayawati%20of%20trying%20to%20erase%20Rajbhar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20history%20by%20changing%20the%20name%20of%20Bhadohi%20district%20to%20Sant%20Ravidas%20Nagar%20and%20only%20promoting%20members%20of%20her%20own%20Jatav%20caste%20to%20the%20neglect%20of%20others%20and%20eventually%20left%20the%20BSP.%20The%20Rajbhars%20believe%20that%20Bhadohi%2C%20a%20district%20adjoining%20Varanasi%20known%20for%20its%20carpet%20industry%2C%20derived%20its%20name%20from%20Bhar%20rulers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20his%20exit%20from%20the%20BSP%2C%20Rajbhar%20joined%20the%20Apna%20Dal%2C%20a%20party%20founded%20by%20Kurmi%20(OBC)%20leader%20Sone%20Lal%20Patel%2C%20who%2C%20like%20him%2C%20had%20been%20an%20associate%20of%20Kanshiram%20in%20the%20BSP.%20Today%2C%20Sone%20Lal%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20party%20and%20family%20are%20split%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20SP.%20Sone%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20younger%20daughter%20Anupriya%20Patel%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Soneylal)%20is%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Modi%20council%20of%20ministers%20and%20a%20key%20BJP%20ally%2C%20while%20his%20elder%20daughter%20Pallavi%20Patel%20is%20an%20SP%20MLA%20from%20Kaushambi.%20Sone%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20widow%20Krishna%20Patel%20heads%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Kameravadi)%2C%20an%20SP%20ally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbhar%2C%20who%20was%20the%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Apna%20Dal%E2%80%99s%20Yuva%20Morcha%2C%20quit%20the%20party%20in%202001%20after%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20Sone%20Lal%2C%20and%20not%20him%2C%20would%20contest%20the%20election%20from%20Kolasla.%20According%20to%20a%20family%20member%20of%20Rajbhar%2C%20actress%20Amisha%20Patel%20was%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20event%20where%20Sone%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20declared%20as%20candidate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20400px)%2085vw%2C%20400px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205611%2FRv8nnqo3_400x400.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205611%2FRv8nnqo3_400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205611%2FRv8nnqo3_400x400-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205611%2FRv8nnqo3_400x400-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663498%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOm%20Prakash%20Rajbhar.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40oprajbhar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFeeling%20a%20sense%20of%20betrayal%20and%20with%20unabashed%20electoral%20ambitions%2C%20Rajbhar%20decided%20to%20form%20his%20own%20party%20in%202002.%20Groomed%20in%20politics%20of%20caste%20icons%2C%20he%20named%20his%20party%20after%20Suheldev%2C%20a%20mythical%20Bhar%20chieftain%20whom%20the%20RSS-BJP%20have%20over%20the%20years%20actively%20projected%20as%20a%20Hindutva%20warrior%20who%20halted%20the%20march%20of%20Muslim%20%E2%80%98invader%E2%80%99%20Ghazi%20Mian%2C%20a%20nephew%20of%20Mahmud%20Ghaznavi.%20That%20Suheldev%E2%80%99s%20historicity%20is%20shrouded%20in%20mystery%20helped%20Rajbhar%20romanticise%20a%20valorized%20past%20for%20his%20community.%20SBSP%E2%80%99s%20distinct%20yellow%20party%20flag%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20colour%20of%20Suheldev%E2%80%99s%20attire.%20Suheldev%20is%20considered%20an%20icon%20by%20both%20Bhars%20and%20Pasis%20(Dalits).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20often-eccentric%20portrayal%20of%20himself%20as%20a%20descendant%20and%20modern%20avatar%20of%20Suheldev%20did%20not%20mean%20much%20for%20the%20SBSP%20electorally.%20Despite%20contesting%20several%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20found%20little%20success.%20In%20the%202012%20Assembly%20election%2C%20the%20SBSP%20contested%2052%20seats%2C%20securing%20over%204%20lakh%20votes%20but%20failed%20to%20open%20its%20account.%20Rajbhar%20himself%20stood%20third.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20in%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20which%20marked%20a%20tectonic%20shift%20in%20state%20and%20national%20politics%2C%20SBSP%20became%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Ekta%20Manch%2C%20a%20front%20that%20included%20the%20Quami%20Ekta%20Dal%20of%20tainted%20politician%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%2C%20today%20designated%20a%20gangster%20by%20the%20Yogi%20government.%20Rajbhar%20contested%20from%20Salempur%20constituency.%20Though%20he%20stood%20fourth%20he%20received%20a%20decent%2066%2C084%20votes%2C%20almost%2025%2C000%20more%20than%20the%20fifth%20placed%20Congress%20candidate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbhar%E2%80%99s%20big%20moment%20came%20in%20June%202016%20when%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20was%20stitching%20together%20a%20rainbow%20of%20non-Yadav%20OBC%20castes%20to%20dethrone%20the%20SP%20in%20UP%2C%20attended%20a%20huge%20rally%E2%80%94Ati-pichda%2C%20Ati-Dalit%20Mahapanchayat%E2%80%94organised%20by%20the%20former%20in%20Mau.%20The%20SBSP%20formally%20entered%20into%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20was%20already%20ruling%20the%20country.%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20relevance%20for%20the%20BJP%20can%20be%20gauged%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20despite%20winning%2073%20out%20of%2080%20seats%20in%202014%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20BJP%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20bring%20on%20board%20a%20second%20ally.%20That%20too%2C%20a%20party%20that%20did%20not%20have%20a%20single%20MLA%20and%20no%20electoral%20record%20to%20boast.%20The%20relationship%2C%20as%20strategized%2C%20would%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20mutually%20beneficial.%20While%20the%20SBSP%20transferred%20its%20support%20base%2C%20mainly%20consisting%20of%20Rajbhars%20and%20associated%20castes%20to%20the%20BJP%20across%20Purvanchal%2C%20and%20underlined%20the%20political%20gap%20between%20Yadavs%20and%20other%20OBCs%2C%20it%20got%20its%20first%20electoral%20success%20in%20the%20form%20of%20four%20MLAs%2C%20including%20Rajbhar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20trounced%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20to%20win%20power%20in%20Lucknow%20in%202017.%20The%20party%20with%20its%20two%20allies%20won%20a%20massive%20majority%E2%80%94325%20out%20of%20403%20seats.%20Rajbhar%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20as%20the%20backward%20classes%20welfare%20minister.%20The%20political%20honeymoon%20period%20did%20not%20last%20long%2C%20as%20Rajbhar%2C%20in%20his%20bid%20to%20carve%20out%20his%20own%20political%20legacy%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98leader%E2%80%99%20of%20backward%20castes%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98loaders%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20started%20confronting%20his%20own%20government.%20By%20loaders%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20OBC%20leaders%20in%20the%20BJP%20who%20toed%20the%20party%20line%20instead%20of%20speaking%20up%20openly%20for%20backward%20caste%20interests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20major%20flash%20point%20was%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20demand%20to%20implement%20the%20recommendations%20of%20a%20social%20justice%20committee%20calling%20for%20sub-categorization%20of%20the%2027%25%20OBC%20quota%20into%20three%20categories.%20This%20would%20benefit%20the%20most-backward%20castes%20including%20his%20own%20community%20which%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report%2C%20would%20be%20in%20the%20most-backward%20category%2C%20consisting%20of%20the%20acutely%20deprived%20OBC%20castes%20having%20limited%20political%20drawing%20power.%20Rajbhar%20had%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%2017%20most%20backward%20castes%20be%20included%20into%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20category.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImplementing%20the%20sub-categorization%2C%20which%20would%20have%20put%20the%20Yadavs%20along%20with%20the%20Kurmis%2C%20Jats%20and%20Gurjars%20in%20the%20same%20category%20and%20reduced%20their%20share%20in%20the%20quota%20to%20a%20mere%207%20out%20of%2027%25%2C%20would%20have%20complicated%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20caste%20calculation.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20was%20to%20attract%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20OBCs%20by%20alienating%20the%20Yadavs%2C%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20core%20support%20base%20and%20the%20single%20largest%20backward%20caste%20in%20the%20state%20in%20terms%20of%20numbers%20and%20political%20clout.%20The%20report%20has%20been%20in%20cold%20storage%20since%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajbhar%20was%20also%20disappointed%20after%20the%20BJP%20refused%20to%20cede%20to%20his%20demand%20of%20granting%20him%20as%20many%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20as%20its%20other%20ally%20the%20Apna%20Dal%2C%20which%20had%20two%20MPs%2C%20in%202019.%20The%20BJP%20offered%20him%20the%20Ghosi%20seat%20in%20East%20UP%20but%20on%20a%20BJP%20symbol.%20Snubbed%20and%20denied%20a%20ticket%20on%20his%20own%20party%20symbol%2C%20Rajbhar%20openly%20rebelled%20and%20intensified%20his%20rhetorical%20attacks%20against%20the%20BJP.%20In%20the%202019%20election%2C%20he%20went%20as%20far%20as%20fielding%20over%2040%20candidates%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20openly%20supported%20the%20Congress%20and%20SP-BSP%20nominees%20on%20some%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20rebellion%20and%20his%20provocative%20remarks%20against%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20and%20exhorting%20his%20support%20to%20thrash%20workers%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%20if%20they%20attempted%20to%20spread%20any%20misinformation%20against%20his%20party%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20take%20any%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20him%20till%20the%20voting%20concluded.%20He%20continued%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20minister%20under%20Adityanath.%20The%20BJP%20did%20not%20want%20to%20alienate%20his%20Rajbhar%20support%20base.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERiding%20on%20the%20popularity%20of%20Modi%2C%20a%20superior%20strategy%20and%20contradictions%20between%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20BSP%2C%20the%20BJP%20comprehensively%20defeated%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMahagathbandhan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20rebellion%20proved%20to%20be%20futile.%20On%20May%2020%2C%202019%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20last%20day%20of%20polling%2C%20the%20axe%20finally%20fell%20on%20him.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Felections%2Fyogi-adityanath-wants-to-drop-up-minister-om-prakash-rajbhar-from-his-cabinet-5737048%2F%5C%22%3EAdityanath%20sacked%20him%20as%20a%20cabinet%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20BJP%20promptly%20promoted%20a%20new%20Rajbhar%20face%2C%20Anil%20Rajbhar%2C%20and%20allotted%20him%20the%20Backward%20Class%20Welfare%20Ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffaced-with-an-opposition-coming-together-bjp-tries-to-balance-the-optics%5C%22%3EFaced%20With%20an%20Opposition%20Coming%20Together%2C%20BJP%20Tries%20to%20Balance%20the%20Optics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20dismissal%2C%20Rajbhar%20did%20not%20abandon%20hope%20and%20went%20on%20to%20form%20yet%20another%20front%E2%80%94Bhagidhari%20Sankalp%20Morcha%2C%20a%20loose%20group%20of%20several%20smaller%20outfits%2C%20mainly%20OBC%2C%20led%20by%20political%20leaders%20in%20the%20wilderness%2C%20including%20outfits%20led%20by%20former%20minister%20Babu%20Singh%20Kushwaha.%20Hyderabad%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%E2%80%99s%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20later%20became%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Morcha%2C%20providing%20it%20with%20its%20much-needed%20Muslim%20factor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20even%20that%20experiment%20fell%20apart%20as%20Rajbhar%2C%20after%20failing%20to%20come%20to%20a%20compromise%20with%20the%20BJP%20whose%20then%20state%20president%20Swatantra%20Dev%20Singh%20he%20regularly%20met%2C%20decided%20to%20warm%20up%20to%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20As%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20was%20attempting%20to%20forge%20a%20large%20alliance%20of%20OBC%20castes%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20dominance%20of%20saffron%2C%20Rajbhar%20added%20%E2%80%98yellow%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20rainbow%20of%20backward%20castes.%20Though%20exact%20figures%20are%20unknown%20in%20absence%20of%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20SBSP%20claims%20that%20Rajbhars%20and%20affiliated%20castes%20form%2018%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20in%20East%20UP%20and%20can%20impact%20126%20Assembly%20units%20in%20different%20degrees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELearning%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20the%20main%20challenger%20to%20Adityanath%20in%202022%2C%20formed%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20SBSP.%20Rajbhar%20was%20also%20promoted%20as%20the%20conductor%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPichdo%20ka%20Inquilab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20(revolution%20of%20the%20backward)%20to%20throw%20out%20the%20BJP%20from%20power.%20In%20October%202021%2C%20on%20the%2019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20foundation%20day%20of%20the%20SBSP%2C%20Akhilesh%20and%20Rajbhar%20formalised%20their%20alliance%20in%20Mau%20with%20a%20massive%20show%20of%20strength%20dubbed%20the%20Vanchit%2C%20Pichda%2C%20Dalit%2C%20Alpsankhyak%2C%20Bhagidhari%20Mahapanchayat%2C%20a%20call%20to%20unite%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Muslim%20voters%20and%20elect%20the%20Yadav%20scion%20as%20chief%20minister%20again.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20Rajbhar%20even%20made%20some%20unsavoury%20comments%20against%20the%20BJP%20top%20leadership%20as%20he%20targeted%20upper%20castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20SBSP%20contested%2019%20seats%20and%20won%20six%2C%20two%20more%20than%20it%20did%20in%202017.%20However%2C%20the%20SP-led%20alliance%2C%20despite%20an%20improved%20performance%2C%20could%20not%20dethrone%20a%20dominant%20BJP.%20With%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20power%2C%20the%20SBSP%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20also%20started%20to%20sour%2C%20with%20Rajbhar%20publicly%20questioning%20Akhilesh%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20skills%20and%20capacity%20to%20work%20hard%20by%20virtue%20of%20him%20being%20a%20dynast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20after%20months%20of%20speculation%2C%20Rajbhar%20finally%20returned%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20where%20his%20party%20icon%20Suheldev%2C%20as%20a%20crusader%20against%20Islamic%20rulers%2C%20fits%20comfortably.%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20support%20is%20bound%20to%20increase%20the%20challenges%20for%20the%20SP%2C%20which%20had%20fared%20decently%20well%20in%20parts%20of%20East%20UP%20in%202022.%20The%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20though%20aware%20that%20Rajbhar%20is%20a%20risky%20bargain%20and%20akin%20to%20unpredictable%20shifts%2C%20has%20displayed%20a%20pragmatic%20approach%20by%20welcoming%20him%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%20Rajbhar%20face%20Anil%20Rajbhar%20lacks%20the%20charisma%20and%20support%20base%20of%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar.%20With%20other%20senior%20Rajbhar%20leaders%2C%20former%20BSP%20state%20president%20Ram%20Achal%20Rajbhar%20and%20the%20son%20of%20former%20UP%20Assembly%20speaker%20Sukhdeo%20Rajbhar%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20SP%2C%20the%20BJP%20must%20have%20felt%20a%20vacuum%20within%20that%20space.%20With%20the%20return%20of%20Rajbhar%2C%20the%20BJP%20gains%20a%20vocal%20OBC%20face%20with%20a%20record%20of%20anti-Yadav%20politics.%20This%20also%20keeps%20its%20other%20two%20allies%2C%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Soneylal)%20and%20the%20Nishad%20Party%2C%20in%20check%2C%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20build%20a%20water-tight%20formula%20for%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20Rajbhar%20gains%20this%20time%20as%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20is%20a%20question%20that%20still%20lingers.%20Will%20he%20finally%20secure%20a%20ticket%20to%20successfully%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20enter%20Parliament%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689521750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16205154%2FFuypJ72WwAgjZTC.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-om-prakash-rajbhars-return-to-nda-mean-for-up-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20months%20of%20speculation%2C%20Rajbhar%20finally%20returned%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20where%20his%20party%20icon%20Suheldev%2C%20as%20a%20crusader%20against%20Islamic%20rulers%2C%20fits%20comfortably.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-om-prakash-rajbhars-return-to-nda-mean-for-up-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Forced%20To%20Outsource%20Islamabad%20Airport%20Due%20To%20Forex%20Crisis%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20continuously%20depleting%20forex%20reserves%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20outsourcing%20the%20operations%20of%20major%20airports.%20The%20finance%20minister%20has%20already%20convened%20multiple%20meetings%20of%20the%20committee%20formed%20to%20engage%20foreign%20operators%20for%20outsourcing%2C%20Dawn%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Ishaq%20Dar%20told%20the%20stakeholders%20to%20finalise%20formalities%20to%20outsource%20the%20operations%20of%20Islamabad%20International%20Airport%20(IIA)%20by%20August%2012%2C%20the%20final%20day%20of%20the%20incumbent%20government's%20term%2C%20Dawn%20reported%20quoting%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDawn%20is%20a%20national%20daily%20of%20Pakistan%20that%20reports%20on%20politics%20and%20current%20affairs%20of%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20steering%20committee%20for%20assessing%20the%20progress%20of%20airport%20operations%20outsourcing%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20privy%20to%20the%20meeting%20told%20Dawn%20that%20the%20committee%20had%20given%20explicit%20instructions%20to%20complete%20the%20necessary%20procedures%20for%20IIA%20outsourcing%20as%20a%20priority%2C%20Dawn%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20announcement%20issued%20after%20the%20meeting%20said%20World%20Bank's%20International%20Finance%20Corporation%20(IFC)%2C%20the%20transaction%20adviser%20for%20the%20outsourcing%2C%20briefed%20the%20meeting%20on%20the%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDar%20wants%20changes%20to%20aviation%20laws%20approved%20before%20month-end.%20The%20meeting%20agreed%20to%20fast-track%20IIA's%20outsourcing%20to%20improve%20service%20delivery%20in%20line%20with%20best%20industry%20practices%2C%20Dawn%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IFC%20also%20gave%20a%20presentation%20to%20the%20committee%20which%20also%20took%20decisions%20on%20the%20future%20roadmap%20of%20outsourcing%20IIA%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2031%2C%20the%20Economic%20Coordination%20Committee%20decided%20to%20kick%20off%20the%2025-year%20outsourcing%20of%20operations%20and%20land%20assets%20at%20Islamabad%2C%20Lahore%2C%20and%20Karachi%20airports.%20Their%20functions%20will%20be%20run%20through%20a%20public-private%20partnership%20to%20generate%20foreign%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Dar%20also%20gave%20a%20deadline%20to%20departments%20concerned%20for%20finalising%20amendments%20to%20civil%20aviation%20laws%20and%20a%20plan%20for%20Pakistan%20International%20Airlines%20(PIA)%20restructuring%2C%20Dawn%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendments%20are%20being%20made%20to%20segregate%20the%20functions%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%2C%20PIA%20and%20Airports%20Security%20Force.%20The%20objective%20is%20to%20eliminate%20overlapping%20responsibilities%20of%20these%20organisations%20by%20enacting%20ordinances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20emphasised%20getting%20amendments%20approved%20by%20the%20parliament%20before%20the%20end%20of%20July.%20This%20timeline%20is%20crucial%20as%20it%20would%20allow%20global%20aviation%20regulators%20to%20dispatch%20inspectors%20in%20August%20for%20an%20on-ground%20assessment%20of%20operational%20systems%20and%20standards%20necessary%20to%20restore%20PIA's%20flights%20to%20the%20US%2C%20UK%20and%20Europe.%20Failure%20to%20meet%20this%20deadline%20would%20result%20in%20a%20year-long%20delay%20before%20the%20inspections%20occur%2C%20Dawn%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPIA's%20flights%20to%20these%20destinations%20have%20been%20suspended%20since%202020%20following%20a%20controversy%20surrounding%20pilots'%20professional%20degrees%20and%20other%20aircraft%20safety%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20chaired%20by%20the%20finance%20minister%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20Federal%20Minister%20for%20Aviation%20and%20Railways%20Saad%20Rafique%2C%20Special%20Assistant%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20Finance%20Tariq%20Bajwa%2C%20the%20Aviation%20Division%20secretary%2C%20Public%20Private%20Partnership%20Authority%20CEO%2C%20PCAA%20director%20general%2C%20IFC%20representatives%20and%20other%20government%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689521220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Fhl723ar8_plane-generic_625x300_21_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-forced-to-outsource-islamabad-airport-due-to-lack-of-forex-reserves-4212793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20continuously%20depleting%20forex%20reserves%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20outsourcing%20the%20operations%20of%20major%20airports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-forced-to-outsource-islamabad-airport-due-to-lack-of-forex-reserves-4212793%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-forced-to-outsource-islamabad-airport-due-to-lack-of-forex-reserves-4212793%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-forced-t