Birkin%2C%20with%20her%20soft%20voice%20and%20androgynous%20silhouette%2C%20quickly%20became%20a%20sex%20symbol%2C%20recording%20a%20steamy%20duo%20with%20a%20growling%20Gainsbourg%20in%201969%2C%20%26quot%3BJe%20t'aime...%20moi%20non%20plus%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanned%20on%20radio%20in%20several%20countries%20and%20condemned%20by%20the%20Vatican%2C%20the%20song%20was%20a%20worldwide%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20and%20I%20became%20the%20most%20famous%20of%20couples%20in%20that%20strange%20way%20because%20of%20'Je%20t'aime'%20and%20because%20we%20stuck%20together%20for%2013%20years%20and%20he%20went%20on%20being%20my%20friend%20until%20the%20day%20he%20died.%20Who%20could%20ask%20for%20more%3F%26quot%3B%20Birkin%20told%20CNN%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20Paris%20became%20my%20home.%20I've%20been%20adopted%20here.%20They%20like%20my%20accent%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Style%20icon%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daughter%20of%20an%20actress%20and%20a%20naval%20officer%2C%20Birkin%20married%20James%20Bond%20composer%20John%20Barry%2C%20with%20whom%20she%20had%20a%20daughter%2C%20Kate.%20The%20marriage%20lasted%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20moved%20to%20France%20after%20meeting%20Gainsbourg%20on%20the%20set%20of%20a%20romantic%20comedy%20in%20which%20he%20was%20her%20co-star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20a%20daughter%2C%20Charlotte%2C%20who%20became%20a%20hugely%20successful%20actress%20and%20singer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20musical%20and%20romantic%20relationship%20between%20Gainsbourg%20and%20Birkin%20was%20famously%20tempestuous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20of%20their%20raging%20rows%2C%20Birkin%20tossed%20herself%20into%20the%20River%20Seine%20after%20throwing%20a%20custard%20pie%20in%20Gainsbourg's%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20blazed%20her%20own%20trail%20after%20walking%20out%20on%20France's%20favourite%20bad%20boy%20in%201980.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20around%2070%20films%20she%20has%20worked%20with%20leading%20directors%20including%20Bertrand%20Tavernier%2C%20Jean-Luc%20Godard%2C%20Alain%20Resnais%2C%20James%20Ivory%20and%20Agnes%20Varda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20remained%20forever%20associated%20with%20Gainsbourg%2C%20who%20continued%20to%20write%20songs%20for%20her%20after%20their%20split%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BLes%20dessous%20chics%26quot%3B%20about%20lingerie%20being%20used%20to%20try%20to%20cover%20up%20a%20relationship%20on%20the%20rocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20most%20beautiful%20song%20about%20separation%20you%20could%20ever%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Birkin%20told%20AFP%20in%20a%202018%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20life%20was%20marked%20by%20tragedy%20and%20obstacles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20oldest%20daughter%2C%20Kate%20Barry%2C%20a%20photographer%2C%20died%20in%20an%20apparent%20suicide%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20fought%20leukaemia%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20and%20in%202021%20suffered%20a%20minor%20stroke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirkin%20is%20survived%20by%20her%20daughter%20with%20Gainsbourg%2C%20Charlotte%2C%20and%20another%20daughter%20Lou%20Doillon%2C%20a%20singer%2C%20from%20a%2013-year%20relationship%20with%20French%20director%20Jacques%20Doillon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689517380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fmouugv0g_jane-birkin-afp-650_625x300_16_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjane-birkin-british-french-celebrity-and-style-icon-dies-at-76-4212799%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jane%20Birkin%2C%20the%20British-born%20singer%20and%20actress%20who%20became%20a%20style%20icon%20in%20her%20adopted%20France%2C%20has%20died%2C%20a%20source%20close%20to%20her%20said%20on%20Sunday.%20She%20was%2076.%22%2C