news%20report%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fthesundaystandard%2F2023%2Fjul%2F16%2Fin-gujarat-33-of-people-very-scared-of-legal-impact-of-political-views-online-2595282.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAHMEDABAD%253A%2520Nearly%2520two%2520out%2520of%2Cfor%2520the%2520Study%2520of%2520Developing%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20NGO%E2%80%99s%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98Status%20of%20Policing%20in%20India%20Report%202023%E2%80%99%2C%20looked%20at%20the%20behaviour%20of%20internet%20users%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20study%2C%20TNIE%20article%20says%2C%20shows%20that%2033%25%20of%20those%20surveyed%20were%20extremely%20scared%20about%20inciting%20legal%20action%20by%20expressing%20their%20political%20opinions%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20study%2C%20while%20most%20respondents%20backed%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20surveillance%20of%20mobile%20phones%20to%20curb%20political%20protests%2C%20many%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20their%20own%20capacity%20to%20openly%20express%20their%20social%20or%20political%20beliefs%20online%20for%20fear%20of%20legal%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20TNIE%2C%20Mahashweta%20Jani%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20coordinator%20of%20%E2%80%98Lokniti%E2%80%99%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20single%20party%20has%20ruled%20for%20a%20long%20time%20in%20a%20state%2C%20the%20overall%20fear%20of%20surveillance%20within%20the%20public%20is%20very%20natural%2C%20due%20to%20autocracy%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20people%20are%20afraid%20to%20express%20their%20political%20opinion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20has%20found%20that%20Gandhinagar%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20the%20survey%2C%20participants%20were%20asked%20if%20they%20are%20afraid%20of%20legal%20action%20if%20their%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20a%20political%20or%20social%20topic%20offend%20certain%20groups.%20Most%20respondents%20said%20yes.%20In%20Gujarat%2C%2033%25%20of%20people%20stated%20they%20are%20very%20scared%20of%20legal%20punishment%20for%20sharing%20political%20or%20social%20opinions%20online.%20Other%2046%25%20said%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Csomewhat%20scared%E2%80%9D.%20Around%209%20%25%20stated%20they%20are%20less%20scared%3B%20while%20only%208%25%20said%20they%20are%20not%20scared%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689506125000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F18143157%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-18-at-2.31.17-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsurvey-finds-33-in-gujarat-are-scared-to-share-political-opinions-online%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20part%20of%20the%20survey%2C%20participants%20were%20asked%20if%20they%20are%20afraid%20of%20legal%20action%20if%20their%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20a%20political%20or%20social%20topic%20offend%20certain%20groups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsurvey-finds-33-in-gujarat-are-scared-to-share-political-opinions-online%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Heat%20storm'%20stretches%20into%20southern%20Europe%2C%20health%20alerts%20issued%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689505871000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101800983%2Cimgsize-130776.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fheat-storm-stretches-into-southern-europe-health-alerts-issued%2Farticleshow%2F101801046.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101801046.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%20Spain%2C%20Italy%20and%20Greece%20have%20been%20experiencing%20scorching%20temperatures%20for%20several%20days%20already%2C%20damaging%20agriculture%20and%20leaving%20tourists%20scurrying%20for%20shade.%20Italy%20has%20issued%20red%20alerts%20for%2016%20of%20its%20cities%20as%20meteorologists%20warn%20that%20temperatures%20will%20hit%20record%20highs%20across%20southern%20Europe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fheat-storm-stretches-into-southern-europe-health-alerts-issued%2Farticleshow%2F101801046.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fheat-storm-stretches-into-southern-europe-health-alerts-issued%2Famp_articleshow%2F101801046.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fheat-storm-stretches-into-southern-europe-health-alerts-issued%2Famp_articleshow%2F101801046.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Faced%20With%20an%20Opposition%20Coming%20Together%2C%20BJP%20Tries%20to%20Balance%20the%20Optics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20180922%2FFwkAAXcWcAQg8uV.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%2024%20opposition%20parties%20are%20set%20to%20meet%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20July%2017%20and%2018%20to%20finalise%20the%20contours%20of%20a%20united%20opposition%20front%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20too%2C%20has%20called%20for%20a%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20meeting%20on%20July%2018.%20The%20NDA%20meet%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20move%20to%20offset%20the%20attention%20the%20opposition%20forces%20have%20been%20getting%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20forces%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20find%20common%20ground%20to%20launch%20a%20united%20campaign%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20ahead%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20polls.%20The%20first%20such%20concerted%20attempt%20was%20made%20on%20June%2023%20in%20Patna%20when%2C%20barring%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20all%20opposition%20parties%20pledged%20to%20chalk%20out%20a%20common%20minimum%20agenda%20for%20the%20opposition%20front.%20The%20AAP%20had%20then%20insisted%20that%20it%20could%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20united%20opposition%20front%20only%20when%20the%20Congress%20formally%20opposed%20the%20controversial%20central%20ordinance%20which%20overturned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20establishing%20powers%20of%20the%20elected%20Delhi%20government%20over%20the%20Delhi%20bureaucracy.%20The%20Congress%2C%20after%20an%20initial%20flip-flop%20over%20the%20ordinance%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20blinked%20ahead%20of%20the%20Bengaluru%20meet.%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-second-opposition-meet-congress-says-it-will-not-support-delhi-ordinance%5C%22%3Eon%20Sunday%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20will%20oppose%20the%20ordinance%20in%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%20beginning%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Modi%20May%20Dismiss%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20Efforts%20To%20Unite%2C%20but%20They%20Are%20Borne%20Out%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hegemony%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-dismiss-oppositions-unity-bjp-hegemony%5C%22%3EModi%20May%20Dismiss%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20Efforts%20To%20Unite%2C%20but%20They%20Are%20Borne%20Out%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hegemony%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenugopal%E2%80%99s%20statement%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20yet%20another%20step%20by%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20to%20conjure%20up%20as%20big%20an%20opposition%20front%20as%20possible%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20joining%20ranks%20with%20arch%20rivals%20who%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20BJP.%20With%20AAP%20now%20likely%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20opposition%20meeting%2C%20the%20two-day%20congregation%20of%20non-BJP%20parties%20is%20all%20set%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20common%20minimum%20agenda%20and%20possibly%20an%20implementable%20seat-sharing%20formula%20in%20different%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20moved%20from%20one%20goal%20post%20to%20another.%20Following%20its%20big%20victory%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20has%20been%20unsparing%20with%20its%20allies%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20complete%20disintegration%20of%20the%20NDA.%20Formidable%20allies%20like%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20other%20smaller%20parties%20have%20left%20the%20NDA%20one%20by%20one%20through%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20second%20tenure%20as%20the%20prime%20minister.%20However%2C%20the%20humiliating%20defeat%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%20and%20more%20recently%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20has%20made%20the%20BJP%20sit%20up%20and%20think%20about%20forging%20a%20pre-poll%20coalition%20to%20challenge%20the%20opposition%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20several%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20pre-poll%20coalition%20to%20win%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20However%2C%20a%20string%20of%20failures%20in%20assembly%20elections%20has%20seemingly%20made%20them%20re-strategise%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20party%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20regional%20parties%20like%20the%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu-led%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20H.D.%20Kumaraswamy-led%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Sukhbir%20Badal-led%20Akali%20Dal%20in%20Punjab%2C%20and%20smaller%20caste-based%20outfits%20led%20by%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20and%20Mukesh%20Sahni%2C%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Pawan%20Kalyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20confidence%20has%20dwindled%20after%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20elections%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Congress%20handed%20it%20a%20comprehensive%20defeat.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20defeat%20has%20also%20possibly%20come%20as%20a%20realisation%20that%20the%20BJP%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20expand%20its%20territorial%20footprint%20at%20all%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20second%20tenure.%20It%20has%20lost%20the%20only%20southern%20state%20Karnataka%2C%20while%20its%20presence%20in%20states%20like%20Telangana%2C%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%20%E2%80%93%20where%20it%20put%20up%20a%20surprisingly%20good%20show%20in%20the%202019%20polls%20%E2%80%93%20has%20only%20become%20weaker.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20the%20NDA%20has%20further%20affected%20its%20electoral%20prospects%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Odisha.%20The%20way%20the%20saffron%20party%20welcomed%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20into%20its%20fold%20indicates%20its%20weak%20footing%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20all%20opposition%20parties%20had%20united%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22A%20Look%20at%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20Lost%20Elections%20and%20Broken%20Alliances%20Amid%20Talks%20on%20Lack%20of%20Opposition%20Unity%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-look-at-the-ndas-lost-elections-and-broken-alliances-amid-talks-on-lack-of-opposition-unity%5C%22%3EA%20Look%20at%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20Lost%20Elections%20and%20Broken%20Alliances%20Amid%20Talks%20on%20Lack%20of%20Opposition%20Unity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindi%20heartland%20is%20the%20only%20bastion%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20still%20on%20a%20strong%20wicket%2C%20especially%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20which%20has%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20exit%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%20from%20the%20MVA%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%2048%20seats%20has%20undoubtedly%20improved%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%20But%20these%20alone%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark.%20Precisely%20because%20of%20such%20factors%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20that%20prided%20itself%20on%20its%20electoral%20strength%2C%20is%20looking%20to%20refuel%20the%20NDA%20by%20reaching%20out%20to%20older%20allies%20that%20it%20had%20no%20hesitation%20in%20deserting%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20holding%20the%20NDA%20gathering%20to%20take%20the%20sheen%20away%20from%20the%20opposition%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20hog%20media%20attention%20and%20keep%20the%20electoral%20race%20competitive.%20Beyond%20the%20optics%2C%20however%2C%20the%20NDA%20remains%20a%20much%20smaller%20coalition%20than%20the%20opposition%20front%20in%20the%20making%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20only%20formidable%20political%20force%20in%20the%20alliance.%20By%20the%20sheer%20virtue%20of%20its%20dominance%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20still%20emerge%20as%20a%20winner%20in%20the%20final%20run.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20authoritarianism%20has%20brought%20traditional%20rivals%20in%20the%20opposition%20ranks%20together%2C%20even%20as%20it%20remains%20too%20distant%20from%20becoming%20a%20truly%20pan-Indian%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689505257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20180922%2FFwkAAXcWcAQg8uV.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffaced-with-an-opposition-coming-together-bjp-tries-to-balance-the-optics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Until%20recently%2C%20several%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20pre-poll%20coalition%20to%20win%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20However%2C%20a%20string%20of%20failures%20in%20assembly%20elections%20has%20s