23071600352_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20two%20ministers%20also%20discussed%20the%20progress%20being%20made%20on%20the%20ongoing%20various%20trade-related%20negotiations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20finance%20ministry%20tweeted%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ffm-sitharaman-discusses-trade-negotiation-progress-with-canadian-dy-pm-123071600352_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ffm-sitharaman-discusses-trade-negotiation-progress-with-canadian-dy-pm-123071600352_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ffm-sitharaman-discusses-trade-negotiation-progress-with-canadian-dy-pm-123071600352_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebrating%20Kerala's%20Renaissance%20Man%2C%20M.T.%20Vasudevan%20Nair%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16150754%2F1280px-M_T_Vasudevan_Nair.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20this%20is%20how%20a%20%E2%80%98child%20of%20%3Cem%3EKarkitakam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20becomes%20%3Cem%3Ekismet%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20(destiny%E2%80%99s)%20child.%20Or%20rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20rarest%20of%20rare%20classical%20instance%20of%20such%20a%20turnaround.%E2%80%9D%20This%20was%20how%20N.%20Gopala%20Krishnan%20(NGK%2C%20as%20his%20friends%20call%20him)%2C%20writer%2C%20translator%20and%20erstwhile%20senior%20administrator%20in%20government%20services%2C%20referred%20to%20the%20media%20coverage%20of%20the%2080th%20birthday%20celebrations%20of%20M.T.%20Vasudevan%20Nair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comment%20was%20made%20in%20a%20private%20conversation%20in%202013%20at%20Kozhikode%2C%20the%20coastal%20town%20in%20north%20Kerala%20where%20NGK%20and%20MT%20resided.%20NGK%20was%20known%20to%20have%20a%20penchant%20for%20adding%20some%20flourish%20or%20a%20bit%20of%20allegory%20to%20normal%2C%20everyday%20conversations.%20Sometimes%2C%20these%20verbal%20exercises%20were%20so%20involved%20that%20they%20used%20to%20go%20above%20the%20heads%20of%20those%20who%20were%20being%20addressed.%20But%2C%20the%20allegory%20in%20his%20comment%20on%20MT%20was%20not%20lost%20on%20the%20audience.%20All%20of%20us%20were%20from%20Kerala%20and%20we%20understood%20what%20Karkitakam%20and%20kismet%20meant%20in%20Malayalam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkitakam%2C%20the%20harshest%20of%20harsh%20monsoon%20months%20was%20synonymous%20with%20penury%20and%20privation%20in%20Kerala.%20Kismet%2C%20a%20word%20shared%20by%20many%20Indian%20languages%20meant%20good%20luck%20or%20positive%20destiny.%20NGK%E2%80%99s%20one-liner%20captures%20MT%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20being%20a%20deprived%20child%20to%20an%20advanced%20age%20with%20tremendous%20material%20and%20intellectual%20successes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENGK%20was%20not%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20explaining%20his%20allegories.%20However%2C%20on%20this%20occasion%2C%20the%20English%20translator%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20last%20novel%20%3Cem%3EVaranasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(published%20in%202003)%2C%20followed%20up%20his%20combination%20of%20%E2%80%9CKarkitakam%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ckismet%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20sort%20of%20solemn%20elucidation.%20He%20said%20that%20MT%E2%80%99s%20life%20as%20well%20as%20his%20birthdays%20have%20a%20trajectory%20marked%20by%20great%20gains%2C%20but%20this%20journey%20was%20by%20no%20means%20smooth%20or%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20reach%20where%20he%20has%2C%20MT%20had%20to%20draw%20copiously%20not%20only%20from%20his%20innate%20and%20vast%20creativity%2C%20but%20also%20go%20through%20sordid%20ordeals%20characterised%20by%20strenuous%20and%20sustained%20physical%20labour.%20It%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20an%20onerous%20journey%20for%20the%20mind%20and%20the%20body.%E2%80%9D%20NGK%20passed%20away%20in%202014%20but%20eight%20years%20later%2C%20in%202022%2C%20his%20allegory%20came%20back%20to%20my%20mind%20when%20I%20read%20about%20yet%20another%20MT%20birthday%20in%20the%20Kerala%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuly%2014%2C%202022.%20On%20this%20day%2C%20MT%20started%20yet%20another%20journey%20by%20road%2C%20from%20his%20house%20in%20Kozhikode%20to%20the%20Malankara%20hills%20in%20central%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Thodupuzha.%20A%20journey%20of%20about%20250%20kilometres%20is%20not%20usually%20very%20long%20but%20it%20is%20arduous%20in%20this%20South%20Indian%20state%20during%20the%20monsoon%20marked%20by%20sporadic%20rains%20of%20varying%20intensity.%20The%20highways%20of%20Kerala%20have%20some%20notoriously%20rough%20patches%20too%2C%20especially%20while%20going%20up%20the%20hills%20of%20Thodupuzha%E2%80%99s%20Malanad%20regions.%20The%20strict%20restrictions%20on%20travel%20and%20social%20interactions%20that%20were%20imposed%20off%20and%20on%20in%20the%20state%20since%20March%202019%2C%20on%20account%20of%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20were%20in%20force%20until%20the%20second%20week%20of%20July%202022.%20Still%2C%20not%20many%20senior%20citizens%20are%20venturing%20out%20to%20travel%2C%20especially%20by%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20official%20records%2C%20on%20July%2015%2C%20the%20very%20next%20day%20of%20his%20journey%2C%20MT%20would%20complete%2089%20years%20of%20age.%20By%20normal%20%E2%80%9Csenior%20citizen%E2%80%9D%20standards%2C%20the%20trip%20would%20have%20been%20quite%20daunting.%20But%2C%20MT%20was%20not%20the%20one%20to%20be%20deterred%20by%20the%20multiple%20factors%20that%20would%20have%20limited%20other%20elders%E2%80%99%20wish%20to%20travel.%20A%20couple%20of%20months%20before%20the%20journey%2C%20he%20was%20afflicted%20with%20various%20ailments%20%E2%80%93%20high%20fever%20and%20chest%20congestion%2C%20which%20would%2C%20presumably%2C%20have%20had%20a%20relatively%20serious%20impact%20given%20his%20long-standing%20diabetes%20and%20unremitting%20%E2%80%98beedi%E2%80%99%20smoking.%20But%2C%20as%20has%20been%20his%20wont%20over%20several%20decades%2C%20MT%20seemed%20to%20have%20overcome%20the%20physical%20strains%20caused%20by%20the%20ailments%20by%20taking%20adequate%20medication%20and%20drawing%20up%20on%20his%20self-generated%20energy%20and%20will%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151104%2FKeralaliteraturefestival_08681.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151104%2FKeralaliteraturefestival_08681.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151104%2FKeralaliteraturefestival_08681-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663455%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EM.%20T.%20Vasudevan%20Nair.%20at%20the%20Kerala%20literature%20festival%20in%202016.%20Photo%3A%20Amarjith%20Mohan%2FWikimedia%20commons%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20he%20left%20Kozhikode%20that%20morning%2C%20took%20a%20short%20break%20for%20lunch%20at%20the%20central%20Kerala%20town%20of%20Thrissur%2C%20and%20went%20up%20the%20hills%20to%20reach%20Thodupuzha%20by%20the%20evening.%20Thankfully%2C%20the%20rains%20had%20not%20hindered%20his%20progress%20through%20the%20day.%20He%20joined%20daughter%20Aswathy%20at%20Thodupuzha%2C%20who%20had%20been%20camping%20there%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20to%20oversee%20the%20production%20of%20one%20of%20the%20episodes%20of%20a%20nine-part%20OTT%20anthology%20movie%20series%20based%20on%20stories%20written%20by%20MT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20on%20July%2015%2C%20MT%20joined%20the%20film%20crew%20at%20the%20shooting%20location%20around%20noon.%20Prominent%20film%20director%20Priyadarshan%20and%20internationally%20renowned%20actor%20Mohanlal%2C%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20welcomed%20MT.%20A%20birthday%20celebration%20of%20sorts%20followed%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccutting%20the%20cake%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20and%20the%20traditional%20Kerala%20%3Cem%3Esadya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(feast).%20A%20very%20unique%20form%20of%20nostalgia%20has%20often%20been%20a%20prominent%20characteristic%20of%20the%20Malayalis%E2%80%99%20socio-cultural%20life%20and%20naturally%20MT%E2%80%99s%20literature%20has%20time%20and%20again%20captured%20and%20reflected%20this%20trait.%20Nostalgia%20was%20an%20overwhelming%20sensation%20for%20almost%20everybody%20on%20the%20sets%20that%20day%2C%20for%20different%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENostalgia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20MT%2C%20the%20story%20being%20filmed%20was%20a%20revisit%20to%20his%20yesteryear.%20It%20was%20%3Cem%3EOlavum%20Threeravum%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Ripples%20and%20Shores)%2C%20which%20had%20been%20originally%20made%20into%20a%20movie%20in%201969.%20MT%E2%80%99s%20screenplay%20was%20then%20directed%20by%20legendary%20Malayalam%20filmmaker%20P.N%20Menon.%20The%20lead%20role%20was%20played%20by%20Madhu%2C%20one%20of%20the%20icons%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema.%20Over%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20writing%20in%20a%20prominent%20Malayalam%20daily%2C%20Priyadarshan%20had%20described%20MT%20as%20the%20personal%20pride%20of%20every%20Malayali.%20In%20the%20same%20breath%20he%20declared%20that%20the%20desire%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmake%20a%20film%20on%20something%20written%20by%20MT%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20most%20intense%20creative%20urge%20that%20he%20had%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20career%20as%20a%20cinema%20director%20had%20begun%20in%20Kerala%20with%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%2C%20but%20in%20due%20course%2C%20he%20had%20moved%20on%20to%20a%20successful%20career%20in%20other%20languages%20and%20film%20industries%20too%2C%20including%20Hindi%20and%20Tamil.%20He%20was%20a%20much%20sought%20after%20director%2C%20but%20he%20himself%20had%20described%20the%20%E2%80%9Cabsence%20of%20an%20MT%20film%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20choking%20void%E2%80%9D%20in%20his%20career.%20Finally%2C%20Priyadarshan%20was%20getting%20to%20fill%20that%20void.%20As%20for%20Mohanlal%2C%20the%20protagonist%20in%20the%20MT%20movie%2C%20some%20of%20the%20stellar%20characters%20that%20helped%20him%20make%20a%20mark%20in%20the%20movies%20through%20a%20career%20lasting%20for%20over%20four%20decades%20were%20written%20by%20MT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20the%20Thodupuzha%20episode%20of%20July%2014%20and%2015%2C%202022%20involving%20other%20creative%20giants%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema%2C%20was%20a%20microcosm%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20own%20life%20and%20journey%20that%20saw%20the%20transformation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9CKarkitakam%E2%80%99s%20child%20into%20a%20destiny%E2%80%99s%20child%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Son%20of%20Karikitakam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkitakam%20is%20the%20month%20of%20intense%20rain%20lasting%20for%20days%20on%20end.%20Dark%20rain%20clouds%20dominate%20the%20skies%20almost%20perennially%20during%20this%20month.%20In%20the%20olden%20times%2C%20the%20rain%20and%20the%20dark%20atmosphere%20created%20by%20it%20practically%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20all%20human%20activity%2C%20including%20professional%20engagements.%20So%20much%20so%2C%20the%20month%20was%20synonymous%20with%20deprivation%20and%20Malayalis%20feared%20this%20leanest%20of%20lean%20months%20the%20most.%20Throughout%20this%20month%2C%20Kerala%20reverberates%20with%20the%20ritualistic%20daily%20reading%20of%20the%20Ramayana.%20Indeed%2C%20divine%20powers%20are%20invoked%20to%20drive%20away%20the%20gloom%2C%20the%20fear%20and%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20the%20season%20of%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20birthdays%20as%20well%20as%20the%20early%20childhood%20that%20Vasu%20(as%20MT%20was%20called%20at%20home)%20had%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20corroborated%20the%20sobriquet%20of%20%E2%80%9CKarkitakam%E2%80%99s%20child%E2%80%9D.%20His%20mother%20Ammalu%20Amma%20had%20serious%20health%20issues%20while%20carrying%20him%20in%20her%20womb.%20There%20was%20even%20a%20medical%20advice%20to%20terminate%20the%20pregnancy.%20This%20was%20attempted%2C%20but%20the%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20did%20not%20succeed.%20Then%2C%20Ammalu%20Amma%20had%20wanted%20a%20girl%20after%20having%20given%20birth%20to%20three%20sons.%20Thus%20Vasu%20was%20essentially%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunwanted%20and%20accidental%E2%80%9D%20child.%20His%20father%20T%20Narayanan%20Nair%20was%20employed%20in%20Ceylon%20and%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20birth.%20Vasu%20would%20see%20him%20for%20the%20first%20time%20only%20after%20he%20had%20crossed%20the%20age%20of%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMT%E2%80%99s%20three%20elders%20brothers%20%E2%80%93%20M.T.%20Govindan%20Nair%2C%20M.T.%20Balakrishnan%20Nair%20and%20M.T.%20Narayanan%20Nair%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20many%20of%20his%20relatives%20have%20recorded%20that%20his%20early%20childhood%20was%20very%20much%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20dark%20and%20uncertain%20elements%20associated%20with%20the%20month%20of%20Karkitakam.%20According%20to%20his%20brothers%2C%20he%20was%20an%20obstinate%20kid%20craving%20for%20attention%20and%20was%20extremely%20difficult%2C%20almost%20rebelliously%20delinquent.%20The%20economic%20travails%20of%20the%20family%20as%20well%20as%20the%20absentee%20father%20working%20in%20far%20off%20lands%20added%20to%20the%20sense%20of%20alienation%20that%20the%20young%20MT%20had.%20MT%20himself%20has%20recorded%20that%2C%20as%20a%20child%2C%20he%20did%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20loss%20at%20not%20getting%20the%20father%E2%80%99s%20affection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVasu%E2%80%99s%20stubbornness%20had%20many%20manifestations%20in%20his%20difficult%20childhood.%20His%20brother%20MTB%20Nair%20recorded%20as%20follows%20in%20an%20article.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20(Vasu)%20would%20cry%20lying%20on%20the%20bed%20when%20he%20woke%20up.%20When%20he%20realised%20crying%20was%20not%20helping%20him%20get%20attention%2C%20he%20would%20come%20to%20the%20kitchen.%20Mother%20would%20have%20work%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20He%20would%20beat%20her.%20She%20would%20strike%20him%20back%20when%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20it%20any%20longer.%20Then%20it%20was%20over.%20He%20would%20beat%20mother%2C%20pinch%20and%20scratch%20her.%20He%20would%20tear%20the%20clothes%20she%20was%20wearing.%20Such%20was%20the%20vehemence%20in%20his%20actions%20that%20people%20who%20came%20home%20would%20wonder%3A%20Oh%20my!%20Why%20does%20this%20child%20behave%20in%20such%20manner!%20What%20does%20sister%20Ammalu%20do%20with%20him%3F%20I%20have%20heard%20mother%20tell%20them%2C%20it%20is%20an%20age%20where%20he%20needs%20affection%20and%20care.%20Do%20I%20have%20time%20for%20it%3F%20Is%20there%20anyone%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMT%E2%80%99s%20birthdays%20came%20and%20went%20but%20were%20never%20celebrated%20in%20childhood.%20The%20birthdays%20of%20his%20brothers%20were%20also%20treated%20with%20same%20indifference%20by%20the%20larger%20family.%20Normally%2C%20the%20sweet%20dish%20called%20%3Cem%3Epayasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20made%20in%20Malayali%20households%20to%20celebrate%20birthdays%2C%20but%20the%20MT%20brothers%20never%20experienced%20this%20pleasant%20culinary%20gift%20in%20their%20childhoods.%20In%20the%20matrilineal%20system%20of%20household%20governance%20that%20existed%20in%20the%20Nair%20households%20such%20as%20MT%E2%80%99s%20during%20that%20period%2C%20the%20controls%20of%20the%20treasury%20and%20granary%20were%20with%20the%20uncles%2C%20who%20allocated%20whatever%20meagre%20supplies%20of%20rice%20and%20other%20essentials%20that%20they%20deemed%20fit%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family.%20Any%20request%20for%20enhancement%20of%20supplies%20was%20met%20with%20severe%20opprobrium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMT%20has%20written%20a%20semi-fictional%20account%20on%20a%20birthday%20situation%20of%20yore.%20The%20story%20titled%20%3Cem%3EOru%20Pirannalinte%20Orma%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(Memory%20of%20a%20Birthday)%20shows%20his%20mother%20fainting%20after%20being%20beaten%20by%20her%20brother%20for%20asking%20extra%20quantity%20of%20rice%20for%20making%20payasam.%20While%20creating%20this%20fictional%20narrative%20loosely%20based%20on%20a%20real%20incident%2C%20MT%20deftly%20delineated%20some%20contours%20of%20his%20depressive%20childhood.%20In%20the%20same%20narrative%2C%20however%2C%20MT%20also%20recorded%20some%20other%20developments%20of%20the%20time%20in%20which%20the%20story%20was%20written%2C%20where%20a%20person%2C%20who%20is%20evidently%20much%20in%20love%20with%20him%2C%20wrote%20as%20follows%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20birthday%20is%20on%20the%20next%20Thursday.%20You%20should%20have%20your%20breakfast%20only%20after%20a%20morning%20bath.%20It%20is%20a%20good%20omen%20that%20it%20is%20Thursday.%20I%20am%20offering%20%3Cem%3EDhara%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Payasam%20(special%20prayers%20and%20sacred%20sweet%20to%20propitiate%20God)%20at%20the%20Shiva%20temple%E2%80%9D.%20This%20narrative%20shows%20that%20finally%2C%20there%20are%20people%20who%20not%20only%20remember%20his%20birthday%20but%20observe%20it%20quietly%20through%20prayers%20and%20offerings%20to%20god.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approbation%20of%20his%20individuality%20as%20well%20as%20his%20social%20being%20kept%20growing%20through%20later%20years.%20And%20in%201992%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20his%2059th%20birthday%2C%20a%20group%20of%20litterateurs%20from%20Kerala%2C%20including%20renowned%20poets%20Sugatha%20Kumari%20and%20O.N.V%20Kurup%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20well%20wishers%20from%20the%20US%20gather%20around%20the%20Niagara%20waterfalls%20to%20celebrate%20it.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20MT%20had%20yet%20another%20birthday%20celebration%20in%20the%20company%20of%20friends%20from%20the%20writers%E2%80%99%20and%20journalists%E2%80%99%20fraternity%2C%20at%20Stratford%20upon%20Avon%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20William%20Shakespeare.%20MT%20himself%20has%20fond%20memories%20of%20this%20celebration%20and%20some%20of%20his%20friends%20rate%20this%20as%20the%20best%20birthday%20the%20maestro%20has%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Sensibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20NGK%20solemnly%20explained%20that%20day%2C%20MT%20had%20reached%20these%20heights%20combining%20his%20immense%20creativity%20and%20intense%20labour.%20This%20combination%20spanned%20diverse%20aspects%20of%20life%2C%20literature%20and%20arts.%20His%20literary%20output%20imparted%20a%20new%20sensibility%20to%20the%20Malayalam%20novel%20and%20the%20short%20story.%20This%20sensibility%20was%20evident%20in%20both%20form%20and%20content%20as%20well%20as%20the%20inexplicable%20beauty%20and%20rhythm%20of%20the%20language%20as%20reflected%20in%20literature.%20Along%20with%20fiction%2C%20he%20made%20forays%20into%20non-fiction%20commentary%20on%20contemporary%20issues%20and%20history.%20This%20too%20had%20his%20distinct%20stamp%20that%20captured%20the%20nuances%20of%20a%20given%20situation%20or%20the%20personalities%20involved%20in%20it%2C%20in%20a%20language%20and%20in%20a%20manner%20without%20parallel.%20In%20short%2C%20MT%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20with%20the%20written%20word%20added%20tremendous%20value%20to%20prose%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20worlds%20of%20MT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20MT%20became%20a%20much%20awarded%20film-maker%2C%20who%20once%20again%20pioneered%20and%20strengthened%20one%20particular%20stream%20of%20the%20neo-realist%20cinema%20in%20India.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20most%20illustrious%20literary%20editor%20that%20the%20journalism%20in%20Kerala%20has%20seen%20in%20its%20history.%20At%20least%20two%20generations%20of%20new%20writers%20owe%20their%20place%20in%20the%20limelight%20to%20this%20truly%20perceptive%20editor%2C%20whose%20journalistic%20endeavors%20not%20merely%20promoted%20Malayalam%20literature%E2%80%99s%20forays%20into%20modernism%20but%20literally%20galvanised%20it.%20Yet%20another%20attribute%20of%20MT%20is%20that%20he%20is%20an%20institution%20builder%2C%20particularly%20of%20cultural%20institutions%20that%20have%20proactively%20sought%20%E2%80%93%20with%20varying%20degrees%20of%20success%20%E2%80%93%20to%20rebuild%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20social%20and%20cultural%20trends%20often%20described%20as%20the%20Kerala%20Renaissance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151452%2FTHUNCHAN_MEMORIAL.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151452%2FTHUNCHAN_MEMORIAL.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151452%2FTHUNCHAN_MEMORIAL-300x146.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22497%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThunchath%20Ezhuthachan%20Memorial.%20Photo%3A%20Vicharam%2FWikimedia%20commons%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20most%20important%20contribution%20in%20this%20regard%20is%20the%20Thunchath%20Ezhuthachan%20Memorial%2C%20at%20Tirur%20in%20north%20Kerala.%20Thunchath%20Ezhuthachan%2C%20considered%20the%20%E2%80%98father%20of%20Malayalam%20language%2C%20not%20only%20evolved%20the%2051-character%20alphabet%20system%20for%20the%20Malayalam%20equivalent%20of%20Sanskrit%2C%20but%20also%20made%20contributions%20to%20refine%20its%20style%20and%20imparted%20to%20it%20an%20%E2%80%98individuality%E2%80%99%20of%20its%20own.%20The%20collective%20effect%20of%20these%20diverse%20streams%20can%20only%20be%20termed%20as%20the%20MT%20phenomenon%2C%20which%20has%20held%20sway%20over%20successive%20generations%20of%20literary%20connoisseurs%2C%20cultural%20aesthetes%20and%20social%20observers%20in%20the%2020th%20and%2021st%20centuries.%20In%20chronological%20terms%2C%20this%20is%20an%20effect%20that%20has%20been%20conspicuous%20right%20through%20the%20nearly%20seven%20decades%20that%20Kerala%20has%20existed%20as%20a%20State%20in%20the%20sovereign%20republic%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20the%20emergence%20of%20this%20%E2%80%98MT%20phenomenon%E2%80%99%20that%20is%20at%20the%20root%20of%20the%20unique%20journeys%20of%20his%20birthday%20and%20the%20way%20its%20celebrations%20have%20evolved%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20three%20decades%20preceding%202023%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20his%2060th%20birthday%20%E2%80%93%20MT%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20is%20observed%20by%20Malayali%20communities%20across%20the%20world.%20Literary%20aficionados%20belonging%20to%20other%20communities%20and%20following%20other%20languages%20also%20become%20part%20of%20the%20celebrations.%20The%20media%20in%20Kerala%2C%20consisting%20of%20newspapers%2C%20portals%20and%20television%20in%20diverse%20languages%2C%20literally%20celebrates%20the%20birthday%20with%20some%20verve.%20Almost%20all%20newspapers%20have%20front-page%20coverages%20referring%20to%20the%20birthday%20and%20all%20other%20forms%20of%20media%2C%20including%20television%20and%20radio%2C%20have%20special%20packages%20of%20stories%20and%20commemorative%20features%20on%20various%20aspects%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20literary%2C%20social%20and%20personal%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20these%20celebrations%20have%20touched%20a%20new%20high%2C%20especially%20because%20MT%20completes%20the%20auspicious%20%3Cem%3Enavathi%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0age%20of%2090.%20There%20are%20other%20reasons%20to%20celebrate%20too.%20The%20year%20also%20marks%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20internationally%20acclaimed%20pathbreaking%20neorealist%20Malayalam%20film%20%3Cem%3ENirmalyam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%2030th%20anniversary%20of%20his%20leadership%20of%20the%20Thunchan%20Memorial%20Trust.%20The%20different%20aspects%20of%20the%20MT%20phenomenon%20are%20also%20being%20celebrated%20through%20a%20series%20of%20events%20highlighting%20the%20landmark%20happenings%20in%20MT%E2%80%99s%20life.%20It%20started%20with%20a%20five-day%20festival%20at%20Thunchan%20Parambu%20titled%20S%3Cem%3Eaadaram%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Respectfully).%20The%20festival%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20on%20May%2016%20and%20the%20inaugural%20event%20was%20attended%20by%20film%20actor%20Mammotty.%20Over%20the%20five-day%20festival%2C%20different%20aspects%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20creative%20life%20%E2%80%93%20novel%2C%20short%20stories%2C%20cinema%2C%20journalism%2Ccultural%20interventions%20and%20institution%20building%20%E2%80%93%20were%20discussed%20from%20a%20historical%20and%20contemporary%20perspective.%20The%20discussion%20on%20MT%E2%80%99s%20novels%20generated%20a%20heated%20debate%20between%20Tamil%20writer%20Jayamohan%20and%20Malayalam%20critic%20M.M.%20Narayanan.%20Jayamohan%20analysed%20MT%E2%80%99s%20novels%20essentially%20as%20stories%20of%20individual%20alienation%20and%20pathos%20while%20Narayanan%20countered%20that%20these%20individual%20stories%20had%20deep%20historical%20and%20political%20dimensions%20too.%20The%20debate%20left%20its%20imprint%20on%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20social%20and%20cultural%20spaces%20for%20days%20on%20end%2C%20underscoring%20the%20continuing%20relevance%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20creative%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emotional%20aspect%20of%20the%20festival%20came%20out%20when%20renowned%20actors%20and%20directors%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema%20recalled%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20MT%20phenomenon%20on%20them.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20dance%20tribute%20to%20MT%20by%20his%20daughter%20and%20renowned%20Bharatnatyam%20danseuse%20Aswathy%20V%20Nair.%20The%20compositions%20were%20based%20on%20the%20songs%20that%20were%20part%20of%20the%20movies%20written%20and%2For%20directed%20by%20MT%20as%20well%20as%20his%20favorite%20verses%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Malayalam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98MT%4090%20celebrations%E2%80%99%20are%20continuing%20with%20different%20publications%20organising%20their%20own%20festivals.%20Mathrubhumi%2C%20the%20media%20house%20with%20considerable%20reach%20among%20Keralaites%20across%20the%20world%2C%20has%20begun%20its%20five%20day%20festival%20on%20July%2010%20at%20Kozhikode.%20It%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20celebrated%20filmmaker%20Maniratnam%20and%20attended%20by%20author%20Manu%20S.%20Pillai.%20%3Cem%3EMalayala%20Manorama%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20largest%20circulated%20Malayalam%20daily%2C%20has%20initiated%20celebrations%20lasting%2090%20days%20on%20July%2014.%20National%20and%20international%20celebrities%20from%20the%20world%20of%20literature%20and%20cinema%20are%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20these%20celebrations%20to%20be%20held%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20top%20it%20all%2C%20the%20year%20would%20also%20witness%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20movie%20productions%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20nine%20short%20stories%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20them%20directed%20by%20a%20clutch%20of%20celebrated%20directors.%20MT%E2%80%99s%20trip%20to%20the%20high%20ranges%20in%202022%20on%20his%2089th%20birthday%20was%20to%20witness%20shoots%20of%20one%20of%20these%20movies.%20Apart%20from%20Olavum%20Threeravum%2C%20Priyadarshan%20is%20directing%20%3Cem%3ESilalikhitham%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Inscriptions)%20too.%20MT%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20also%20makes%20her%20directorial%20debut%20in%20this%20series%20with%20%3Cem%3EVilpana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20Sale).%20Other%20movies%20in%20the%20series%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20directors%20are%20as%20follows.%3Cem%3E%20Abhayam%20Thedi%20Veendum%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Once%20again%2C%20In%20Search%20of%20Refuge%2C%20Santosh%20Sivan%20)%2C%20%3Cem%3ESwargam%20Thurakkunna%20Samayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(When%20the%20Doors%20of%20Heaven%20Open%2C%20Jayaraj%20)%2C%20%3Cem%3EKazhcha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Vision%2C%20Shyama%20Prasad)%2C%20%3Cem%3EKadalkkaattu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Sea%20Breeze%2C%20Rathish%20Ambat)%2C%20%3Cem%3ESherlock%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Mahesh%20Narayanan)%2C%20%3Cem%3EKadugannava%20Oru%20Yathra%20Kurippu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Kadugannava%2C%20A%20Travel%20Note%2C%20Ranjith).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20what%20is%20being%20celebrated%20across%20the%20Malayali%20universe%20is%20not%20MT%E2%80%99s%20actual%20birthday.%20July%2015%2C%20the%20date%20that%20is%20marked%20as%20MT%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20is%20one%20that%20was%20ascribed%20by%20an%20uncle%20of%20his%20while%20getting%20him%20admitted%20to%20an%20school%20before%20the%20permissible%20age%20of%20admission.%20In%20the%20initial%20years%20of%20his%20life%2Cthis%20oversight%20did%20not%20matter%20as%20there%20was%20no%20scope%20for%20birthday%20celebrations%20on%20account%20of%20colossal%20constraints%20of%20resources%20and%20social%20mobility.%20Later%2C%20the%20wrong%20date%20was%20widely%20acknowledged%20and%20honoured.%20Talking%20about%20this%20to%20me%2C%20MT%20had%20said%20at%20this%20later%20stage%20too%2C%20there%20was%20no%20urge%20to%20correct%20the%20mistake%2C%20because%20signifying%20birthdays%20was%20not%20a%20primary%20concern%20for%20him.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20indicated%20that%20his%20was%20an%20approach%20that%20sought%20to%20paraphrase%20Shakespeare%E2%80%99s%20famous%20quote%20%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20a%20name%3F%20That%20which%20we%20call%20a%20rose%2FBy%20any%20other%20name%20would%20smell%20as%20sweet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20the%20record%20straight%2C%20MT%E2%80%99s%20real%20date%20of%20birth%20is%20not%20July%2015%2C%20but%20August%209.%20A%20majority%20of%20those%20who%20have%20sought%20to%20chronicle%20parts%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20life%20with%20some%20precision%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar%20was%20not%20followed%20in%20MT%E2%80%99s%20ancestral%20home.%20The%20norm%20was%20to%20follow%20the%20Malayalam%20%E2%80%9CKolla%20Varsham%20%E2%80%9Ccalendar.%20As%20per%20this%20calendar%2C%20MT%20was%20born%20on%20Uthrattathi%20day%20in%20Karkitakam%20in%20the%20Kolla%20Varsham%201108.%20This%20was%20the%2025th%20day%20of%20Karkitakam%20that%20year.%20MT%20says%20that%2C%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20his%20life%20no%20one%20really%20cross%20checked%20the%20corresponding%20date%20on%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20cross-checking%20was%20done%20decades%20later%2C%20around%20the%20mid-1960s%2C%20after%20MT%20had%20become%20a%20celebrated%20Malayalam%20writer.%20Even%20when%20the%20cross-checking%20was%20done%2C%20the%20unique%20methods%20of%20calculation%20of%20days%20and%20months%20in%20the%20Kolla%20Varsham%20calendar%20created%20their%20own%20quirky%20results.%20Thus%2C%20the%20corresponding%20date%20in%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar%20was%20shown%20as%20August%208%20as%20per%20some%20calculations%20and%20as%20August%209%20in%20some%20others.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20serious%20effort%20to%20rationalise%20the%20different%20dates%2C%20in%20all%20probability%2C%20following%20the%20paraphrased%20Shakespearean%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20a%20date%E2%80%9D%20logic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20same%2C%20since%20the%20date%2015th%20of%20July%20was%20entered%20in%20application%20forms%20while%20getting%20admitted%20to%20school%20as%20a%20kid%2C%20the%20date%20has%20got%20stuck.%20Not%20just%20in%20official%20records%2C%20but%20in%20the%20collective%20social%20memory%20of%20Keralites%20as%20a%20whole.%20And%20year%20after%20year%2C%20the%20media%20celebrates%20this%20collective%20consciousness.%20July%202023%20is%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaidem.com%2Fmt-vasudevan-nair-child-of-karkitakam%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20The%20AIDEM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689501983000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16150754%2F1280px-M_T_Vasudevan_Nair.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fcelebrating-keralas-renaissance-man-m-t-vasudevan-nair%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20two%20generations%20of%20new%20writers%20owe%20their%20place%20in%20the%20limelight%20to%20this%20truly%20perceptive%20editor%2C%20whose%20journalistic%20endeavors%20not%20merely%20promoted%20Malayalam%20literature%E2%80%99s%20forays%20into%20modernism%20but%20literally%20galvanised%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fcelebrating-keralas-renaissance-man-m-t-vasudevan-nair%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Net%20debt%20of%20top%208%20listed%20realty%20firms%20dip%2043%25%20in%20last%203%20years%3A%20Anarock%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689501011000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-12%2F22%2Ffull%2F1671682054-7138.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnet-debt-of-top-8-listed-realty-firms-dip-43-in-last-3-years-anarock-123071600337_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20average%20cost%20of%20debt%20for%20these%20eight%20players%20fell%20to%209%25%20in%20FY23%20from%2010.3%25%20in%20FY20.%20In%202020-21%2C%20the%20interest%20cost%20was%209.05%25%2C%20while%20the%20cost%20of%20debt%20was%207.96%25%20in%202021-22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnet-debt-of-top-8-listed-realty-firms-dip-43-in-last-3-years-anarock-123071600337_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnet-debt-of-top-8-listed-realty-firms-dip-43-in-last-3-years-anarock-123071600337_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnet-debt-of-top-8-listed-realty-firms-dip-43-in-last-3-years-anarock-123071600337_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Is%20France%20So%20Eager%20to%20Cosy%20Up%20to%20an%20Authoritarian%20Narendra%20Modi%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16150816%2FF1BDWMXaAAAcB-i.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%3C%2Fspan%3Endia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20economic%20relationship%20with%20France%20is%20different%20from%20other%20comparable%20countries%20in%20one%20key%20area%3A%20their%20bilateral%20trade%20in%20goods.%20While%20Germany%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20recorded%20significant%20volumes%20%E2%80%93%20%2425bn%20and%20%2417bn%20respectively%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20France%E2%80%99s%20total%2C%20excluding%20military%20sales%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india-briefing.com%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20just%20over%20%2412bn%3C%2Fa%3E.%20French%20businesses%20are%20less%20well%20established%20in%20India%20than%20those%20from%20other%20European%20countries%2C%20with%20a%20few%20high-profile%20exceptions%20such%20as%20Capgemini%2C%20a%20technology%20services%20and%20consulting%20firm%2C%20half%20of%20whose%20350%2C000%20workers%20are%20employed%20there.%20But%20France%20ranks%2011th%20among%20foreign%20investors%20in%20India%2C%20while%20the%20Netherlands%20is%20fourth%2C%20and%20Germany%2C%20a%20commercial%20power%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20comes%20ninth%2C%20with%20200%20Indian%20investors%20active%20in%20Germany.%20Likewise%2C%20despite%20efforts%20by%20the%20French%20authorities%20and%20academics%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20students%20on%20French%20campuses%20%E2%80%93%20around%20ten%20thousand%20%E2%80%93%20lags%20far%20behind%20Germany%2C%20which%20had%2034%2C000%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driving%20force%20of%20Franco-Indian%20relations%20is%20elsewhere%2C%20in%20the%20sovereign%20realm%20of%20strategy%2C%20and%20indeed%20security%2C%20where%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20role%20is%20greater%20than%20in%20the%20economy.%20Both%20countries%20justify%20their%20closeness%20as%20being%20in%20their%20national%20interest%2C%20invoking%20the%20%E2%80%98democratic%20values%E2%80%99%20they%20supposedly%20share.%20Yet%20India%E2%80%99s%20recent%20political%20evolution%20completely%20undermines%20this.%20So%20where%20do%20France%E2%80%99s%20short-%20and%20long-term%20interests%20really%20lie%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrance%E2%80%99s%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeopolitically%2C%20India%20has%20long%20been%20France%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20partner%20%E2%80%93%20officially%20since%20January%201998%2C%20when%20Jacques%20Chirac%20made%20a%20historic%20presidential%20visit%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20lacked%20a%20stable%20government%20and%20was%20just%20weeks%20from%20the%20election%20that%20brought%20to%20power%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20the%20first%20Hindu%20nationalist%20prime%20minister%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20Soon%20after%2C%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20nuclear%20tests%20were%20widely%20condemned%20by%20the%20international%20community%20(India%20has%20never%20signed%20the%20Non-Proliferation%20Treaty)%2C%20but%20not%20by%20France.%20The%20US%2C%20Japan%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20UK%20and%20many%20other%20countries%20imposed%20sanctions%2C%20but%20France%20showed%20an%20indulgence%20that%20India%20still%20remembers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20context%2C%20this%2025-year-old%20strategic%20partnership%20has%20taken%20on%20increased%20importance%20because%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20rise%2C%20particularly%20as%20manifested%20by%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20influence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20Countries%20in%20the%20region%2C%20such%20as%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20which%20have%20taken%20on%20loans%20from%20Chinese%20lenders%20for%20large-scale%20projects%2C%20now%20find%20their%20sovereignty%20weakened.%20France%2C%20as%20a%20resident%20power%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20where%20much%20of%20its%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%20(EEZ)%20is%20located%20because%20of%20its%20overseas%20territories%2C%20is%20concerned%20about%20this%20expansionism.%20So%20is%20New%20Delhi%2C%20to%20an%20even%20greater%20extent%2C%20as%20it%20is%20beginning%20to%20feel%20encircled%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20Chinese%20presence%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Nepal%20and%20Bangladesh.%20These%20mutual%20interests%20in%20the%20region%20partly%20explain%20India%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20France%E2%80%99s%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%2C%20first%20presented%20by%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20in%20May%202018%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20Sydney%2C%20in%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondediplo.com%2F2021%2F06%2F08bulard%5C%22%3Ehe%20described%20China%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20in%20the%20region%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98gamechanger%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20official%20statements%20on%20the%20subject%20present%20India%20as%20France%E2%80%99s%20key%20partner%20in%20the%20region%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20trilateral%20dialogues%20that%20France%20and%20India%20have%20had%20with%20Australia%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE).%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20helped%20Paris%20gain%20membership%20to%20multilateral%20(or%20%E2%80%98minilateral%E2%80%99)%20bodies%20on%20account%20of%20its%20extensive%20maritime%20footprint%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Rim%20Association%20(IORA)%2C%20which%20it%20joined%20in%202020.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20bilateral%20military%20manoeuvres%2C%20the%20earliest%20of%20which%2C%20Varuna%2C%20has%20been%20an%20annual%20event%20since%202001%3B%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20Cl%C3%A9menceau%20took%20part%20in%20it%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20position%20of%20the%20French%20government%2C%20which%20regards%20India%20as%20its%20preferred%20partner%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20particularly%20to%20resist%20China%E2%80%99s%20inroads%2C%20is%20worth%20examining.%20Academic%20Ashley%20Tellis%20is%20one%20of%20those%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Findia%2Famericas-bad-bet-india-modi%5C%22%3Einitiated%20this%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%99%20relations%20with%20India.%20He%20has%20argued%20that%20Washington%2C%20where%20Narendra%20Modi%20made%20a%20state%20visit%20in%20June%2C%20%E2%80%98has%20made%20an%20enormous%20bet%E2%80%99%20on%20India%2C%20treating%20it%20as%20a%20key%20partner%20simply%20because%20the%20US%20has%20neither%20the%20means%20nor%20inclination%20to%20confront%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20view%20is%20supported%20by%20three%20facts.%20First%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20is%20much%20weaker%20than%20China%E2%80%99s%2C%20its%20largest%20trading%20partner%2C%20on%20which%20it%20is%20heavily%20reliant.%20Second%2C%20New%20Delhi%20prefers%20not%20to%20react%20to%20China%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20encroachment%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20which%20is%20visible%20in%20satellite%20images%2C%20to%20avoid%20initiating%20hostilities%20in%20which%20India%20would%20come%20off%20worse.%20Third%2C%20India%20and%20China%20continue%20to%20collaborate%20within%20BRICS%20(Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20South%20Africa)%20to%20dislodge%20Western%20powers%20from%20their%20positions%20of%20power%20in%20the%20UN%20system%2C%20mainly%20because%20both%20reject%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20vision%20of%20the%20liberal%20international%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20read%20the%20rest%20of%20this%20article%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondediplo.com%2F2023%2F07%2F14india-france%5C%22%3ELe%20Monde%20diplomatique%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20first%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondediplo.com%2F%5C%22%3EEnglish%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monde-diplomatique.fr%2F%5C%22%3EFrench%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%20Le%20Monde%20diplomatique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChristophe%20Jaffrelot%20is%20a%20senior%20research%20fellow%20at%20CERI-Sciences%20Po%2FCNRS%2C%20Paris%2C%20Professor%20of%20Indian%20Politics%20and%20Sociology%20at%20King%E2%80%99s%20India%20Institute%2C%20London%2C%20and%20non-resident%20scholar%20at%20the%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689500353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16150816%2FF1BDWMXaAAAcB-i.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffrance-emmanuel-macron-narendra-modi-strategy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20driving%20force%20of%20Franco-Indian%20relations%20is%20elsewhere%2C%20in%20the%20sovereign%20realm%20of%20strategy%2C%20and%20indeed%20security%2C%20where%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20role%20is%20greater%20than%20in%20the%20economy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffrance-emmanuel-macron-narendra-modi-strategy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tom%20Cruise%E2%80%99s%20most%20stunning%20stunts%20in%20MI7%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689499800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101783100%2Cimgsize-47952.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Ftom-cruises-stunning-stunts-in-mission-impossible-dead-reckoning-part-one%2Fphotostory%2F101783100.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101783100.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3Etom%20cruise%E2%80%99s%20stunning%20stunts%20in%20mission%3A%20impossible%20-%20dead%20reckoning%20part%20one%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arjun%20Pereira%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Ftom-cruises-stunning-stunts-in-mission-impossible-dead-reckoning-part-one%2Fphotostory%2F101783100.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saxophonist%20Wayne%20Shorter%20Changed%20History%20%E2%80%93%20Sometimes%20Consciously%2C%20Sometimes%20Not%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16142752%2F2801307405_36e6652c07_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%E2%80%99s%20been%20hijacked%20from%20the%20cradle%2C%20but%20some%20turtles%20will%20make%20it%20to%20the%20sea.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E%E2%88%BC%20Wayne%20Shorter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20guess%20you%20can%20blame%20Wayne%20Shorter%20for%20making%20legions%20of%20rock-and-roll%20fans%20believe%20they%20were%20actually%20listening%20to%20jazz%2C%20when%20he%20took%20a%20solo%20on%20Steely%20Dan%E2%80%99s%20tune%20Aja%2C%20back%20in%201977.%20But%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20because%20of%20some%20deeply%20thought-out%20decision%20by%20Shorter%2C%20to%20misappropriate%20the%20ears%20of%20rock-and-rollers.%20The%20truth%20is%20rather%20banal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewmusicusa.org%2Fnmbx%2Fnotes-from-the-custerdome-a-jazz-appreciation-of-steely-dan%2F%5C%22%3Einterview%20by%20Eugene%20Holley%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20NewMusicUsa.org%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20this%20piece%20(%E2%80%98Aja%E2%80%99)%2C%20which%20had%20this%20long%20modal%20section%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fagen%20(%3Cem%3EDonald%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Steely%20Dan%3C%2Fem%3E)%20proudly%20told%20me%20in%20my%20interview%20with%20him%20in%202013.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98who%20would%20be%20the%20ideal%20person%20for%20the%20track%3F%E2%80%99%20And%20we%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Wayne%20Shorter.%E2%80%99%20On%20the%20first%20try%2C%20he%20said%20no.%20But%20we%20knew%20someone%20who%20knew%20him%2C%20and%20he%20asked%20him%2C%20because%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20we%20were.%20So%20we%20sent%20him%20the%20track%2C%20and%20he%20liked%20it%20and%20decided%20to%20come%20in.%20And%20he%20nailed%20it%20on%20the%20first%20take.%20That%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20moments%20for%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusicians%2C%20like%20other%20professionals%2C%20are%20for%20hire.%20And%20sometimes%20they%20change%20the%20course%20of%20history%20without%20meaning%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWayne%20Shorter%20significantly%20influenced%20the%20way%20jazz%20bifurcated%20from%20bebop%2C%20a%20complex%20and%20virtuosic%20form%20of%20music%20dominating%20the%20scene%20in%20the%20late%20%E2%80%9950s%20and%20%E2%80%9960s%2C%20to%20the%20more%20accessible%20jazz%20fusion%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9970s.%20Not%20merely%20as%20a%20sax-for-hire%20with%20Steely%20Dan%20or%20Joni%20Mitchell%2C%20but%20in%20a%20deliberate%20and%20conscious%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20part%20of%20a%20movement%20that%20was%20taking%20place%20in%20New%20York%20City%20which%20began%20with%20Miles%20Davis.%20Davis%20was%20at%20the%20time%20the%20most%20significant%20and%20influential%20jazz%20musician%20in%20the%20whole%20world.%20If%20you%20got%20a%20gig%20playing%20with%20Miles%2C%20your%20career%20was%20pretty%20much%20made.%20Shorter%E2%80%99s%20biographer%20Michelle%20Mercer%20recalls%20what%20he%20said%20about%20the%20first%20time%20he%20played%20on%20stage%20with%20Davis.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20like%20a%20cello%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20viola%2C%20I%20felt%20liquid%2C%20dot-dash%2C%20and%20colours%20started%20really%20coming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShorter%20played%20in%20his%20band%20from%20the%20mid%20%E2%80%9960s%20to%20the%20early%20%E2%80%9970s.%20Davis%20was%20focused%20on%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20enormous%20audiences%20generously%20funding%20the%20rock%2C%20folk%20and%20funk%20steamroller%20of%20the%20day.%20His%20way%20was%20to%20create%20a%20simpler%2C%20groove%20based%2C%20swayable%20type%20of%20music%20with%20way%20fewer%20chord%20changes.%20It%20naturally%20allowed%20the%20inclusion%20of%20many%20more%20fans%20who%20easily%20found%20relatable%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20404px)%2085vw%2C%20404px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16142635%2FWayne-Shorter_in_Amsterdam_1980.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22404%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16142635%2FWayne-Shorter_in_Amsterdam_1980.jpeg%20647w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16142635%2FWayne-Shorter_in_Amsterdam_1980-190x300.jpeg%20190w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663444%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22639%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWayne%20Shorter%20playing%20with%20Weather%20Report%2C%20Amsterdam%2C%201980.%20Photo%3A%20Chris%20Hakkens%2FCC%20BY%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Miles%E2%80%99%20Bitches%20Brew%20was%20released%2C%20it%20was%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20the%20stellar%20band%20members%20all%20branched%20out%20on%20their%20own%20creating%20a%20powerful%20jazz%20fusion%20age.%20The%20most%20famous%20of%20them%20were%20John%20McLaughlin%20(Mahavishnu%20Orchestra)%2C%20Chick%20Corea%20(Return%20to%20Forever)%2C%20Wayne%20Shorter%20and%20Joe%20Zawinul%20(Weather%20Report).%20There%20were%20many%20others%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShorter%20came%20from%20a%20solid%20bebop%20background%20and%20you%20can%20hear%20this%20in%20his%20phrasing%2C%20even%20during%20the%20Weather%20Report%20era.%20But%20he%20wanted%20to%20shed%20that%20persona%20and%20believe%20in%20what%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20create.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20not%20into%20composition.%20I%E2%80%99m%20into%20decomposition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20once%20told%20musician%20Jason%20Moran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lyrical%20and%20vocal%20quality%20to%20his%20soloing%2C%20which%20is%20perhaps%20why%20through%20his%20career%20he%20has%20collaborated%20with%20vocalists.%20Something%20that%20makes%20my%20heart%20sing.%20I%20loved%20his%20album%20Native%20Dancer%20with%20Milton%20Nascimento%20released%20in%201975.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20the%20kind%20of%20bossa%20nova%20that%20sells%3F%20%E2%80%98Girl%20From%20Ipanema%E2%80%99%20that%20kind%20of%20thing%3F%20Well%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20ok%E2%80%A6%20but%20he%20(%3Cem%3ENascimento%3C%2Fem%3E)%20was%20coming%20from%20the%20underpinnings%20of%20molte-something%2C%20the%20Amazon%20and%20Africa%20and%20everything%2C%20and%E2%80%A6%20he%20had%20another%20sound%20in%20his%20voice.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20like%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20be%20someone%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shorter%20told%20Christian%20McBride%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mid%201970s%20is%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20City%20and%20took%20my%20own%20stab%20at%20the%20jazz%20scene%20there.%20I%20was%20playing%20with%20Ryo%20Kawasaki%2C%20a%20Japanese%20jazz%20guitar%20player%20with%20amazing%20chops%20and%20a%20lovely%20sense%20of%20where%20music%20was%20headed.%20We%20made%20a%20couple%20of%20albums%20together.%20He%20was%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gil%20Evans%20Orchestra%20and%20Elvin%20Jones%E2%80%99%20band.%20One%20day%20he%20told%20me%20that%20Wayne%20Shorter%20and%20Weather%20Report%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20singer%20and%20that%20he%20had%20sent%20them%20some%20music%20that%20we%20had%20recorded%20together.%20I%20was%20kind%20of%20taken%20aback%20and%20mostly%20started%20to%20panic.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20if%20I%20could%20do%20it%20and%20really%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20idea%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20huge%20surprise%20Shorter%20called%20me%20one%20afternoon%2C%20probably%20around%201978%20or%201979%2C%20and%20we%20talked%20for%20a%20while%20on%20the%20phone.%20He%20said%20he%20really%20liked%20my%20singing%20and%20was%20considering%20a%20vocalist%20for%20the%20band.%20Nothing%20happened%20after%20that%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%2C%20because%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20ready%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201993%20my%20friend%2C%20jazz%20vocalist%20and%20fellow%20Ryo%20Kawasaki%20alumnus%20Clare%20Forster%2C%20made%20an%20entire%20album%20of%20his%20music%20called%2C%20%E2%80%98Clare%20Forster%20Sings%20Wayne%20Shorter.%E2%80%99%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20beautiful%20tribute%20to%20him%20and%20the%20singing%20is%20just%20magnificent.%20She%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20many%20years%20I%20have%20been%20a%20great%20admirer%20of%20Wayne%20Shorter%E2%80%99s%20compositions.%20His%20raw%2C%20human%20sound%20through%20the%20saxophone%20first%20drew%20me%20to%20his%20music.%E2%80%9D%20Perhaps%20deliberately%2C%20she%20leaves%20out%20Footprints%2C%20Shorter%E2%80%99s%20most%20famous%20tune%20and%20one%20that%20has%20been%20widely%20covered%20by%20many%20musicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%202021%20and%20Wayne%20Shorter%2C%20age%2088%20has%20collaborated%20with%20the%20Harvard%20professor%2C%20Grammy-winning%2C%20bass%20player%20and%20vocalist%20Esperanza%20Spalding%20to%20produce%20an%20enormous%20piece%20of%20work%20named%20Ephigenia.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20opera%20that%20took%20eight%20years%20to%20make%20and%20involved%20all%20sorts%20of%20obstacles%20and%20challenges.%20Luckily%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20stage%20multiple%20performances%20before%20Wayne%20Shorter%20took%20his%20final%20encore%2C%20saying%20to%20the%20audience%2C%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20is%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20try%20to%20keep%20and%20go%20forward%20with.%20Nothing.%20Thank%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERIP%20Wayne.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.radhathomas.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERadha%20Thomas%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20jazz%20vocalist%2C%20composer%20and%20author.%20She%20lives%20in%20Bangalore%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689497920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16142752%2F2801307405_36e6652c07_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fsaxophonist-wayne-shorter-changed-history-sometimes-consciously-sometimes-not%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wayne%20Shorter%20significantly%20influenced%20the%20way%20jazz%20bifurcated%20from%20bebop%2C%20a%20complex%20and%20virtuosic%20form%20of%20music%20dominating%20the%20scene%20in%20the%20late%20'50s%20and%20'60s%2C%20to%20the%20more%20accessible%20jazz%20fusion%20of%20the%20'70s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fsaxophonist-wayne-shorter-changed-history-sometimes-consciously-sometimes-not%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20says%20Russia%20has%20'sufficient'%20cluster%20munitions%20for%20tit-for-tat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689497485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101798813%2Cimgsize-72274.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fputin-says-russia-has-sufficient-cluster-munitions-for-tit-for-tat%2Farticleshow%2F101798839.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101798839.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fputin-says-russia-has-sufficient-cluster-munitions-for-tit-for-tat%2Farticleshow%2F101798839.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fputin-says-russia-has-sufficient-cluster-munitions-for-tit-for-tat%2Famp_articleshow%2F101798839.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fputin-says-russia-has-sufficient-cluster-munitions-for-tit-for-tat%2Famp_articleshow%2F101798839.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Narendra%20Modi%20Knows%20an%20Actual%20UCC%20Will%20Be%20an%20Electoral%20Disaster%20for%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F09092822%2FIMG_1682.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20all%20cousins%20be%20allowed%20to%20marry%2C%20or%20nieces%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fstate%2Fsc-declines-to-recognise-marriage-with-maternal-uncle-776627.html%5C%22%3Ematernal%20uncles%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Or%20will%20that%20be%20banned%20for%20all%20in%20the%20new%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%2C%20including%20those%20communities%20currently%20exempted%20from%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%E2%80%99s%20ban%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fedit-page%2Fa-question-of-balance%2Farticleshow%2F5941357.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98sapinda%E2%80%99%20marriages%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Will%20we%20all%20have%20to%20follow%20Christian%20family%20law%20when%20we%20wish%20to%20divorce%3F%20Will%20rules%20from%20the%20Muslim%20personal%20code%20apply%20as%20regards%20inheritance%20and%20sharing%20of%20property%20with%20parents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1051903%2Fagnates-cognates-half-bloods-and-full-bloods-the-real-challenge-in-drafting-a-uniform-civil-code%5C%22%3Eif%20one%20dies%20intestate%20or%20perhaps%2C%20Parsi%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Will%20everyone%20be%20allowed%20to%20avail%20of%20the%20attractive%20tax%20benefits%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Undivided%20Family%20(HUF)%3F%20Or%20will%20that%20be%20abolished%20for%20all%2C%20uniformly%3F%20Will%20all%20Indians%20be%20forced%20to%20follow%20Santhal%20customs%3F%20Or%20Naga%20ones%3F%20(By%20the%20way%2C%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fshow-data%3Factid%3DAC_CEN_5_23_000010_197402_1517807320555%26orderno%3D1%5C%22%3ECode%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201973%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20Nagaland%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20is%20known%20as%20there%20is%20no%20publicly%20available%20draft%20of%20a%20UCC%20being%20talked%20up%20by%20the%20BJP.%20What%20we%20know%20is%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20dislikes%20diversity%20and%20sees%20diverse%20practices%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20Indian%20Union.%20It%20said%20so%20in%20its%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20October%202022%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20petition%20on%20the%20UCC.%20The%20Union%20government%20said%20that%20citizens%20belonging%20to%20different%20religions%20and%20denominations%20adhering%20to%20different%20property%20and%20matrimonial%20laws%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-files-affidavit-on-uniform-civil-code-in-sc-says-different-religions-following-different-laws-affronting-national-unity%2Farticle66026485.ece%5C%22%3Ean%20%E2%80%9Caffront%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20unity%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20month%20too%20referred%20to%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20laws%20for%20separate%20communities%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20the%20country%20could%20not%20run%20on%20a%20dual%20system.%20Oddly%2C%20this%20was%20not%20in%20some%20meeting%20or%20address%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20but%20while%20addressing%20booth-level%20workers%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bhopal.%20It%20is%20clearly%20in%20an%20electoral%20context%20that%20the%20UCC%20is%20being%20referred%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20where%20the%20catch%20is.%20The%20BJP%20may%20be%20picking%20on%20an%20electorally%20indigestible%20bone.%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20attempts%20to%20suddenly%20spring%20a%20UCC%20on%20all%20Hindus%20too%20would%20be%20a%20disaster.%20Maybe%20that%20is%20why%20there%20is%20no%20draft.%20In%20Uttarakhand%2C%20for%20example%2C%20where%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20by%20the%20BJP%20state%20government%20under%20Justice%20(retd)%20Ranjana%20Desai%2C%20to%20work%20one%20out%20for%20the%20state%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbehind-uttarakhand-ucc-13-months-of-consultations-38-public-meetings-8697983%2F%5C%22%3E13%20months%20of%20consultations%2C%2038%20public%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20no%20report%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emphasis%20is%20on%20uniformity%20and%20not%20progressive%20or%20better%20or%20emancipatory.%20So%2C%20what%20or%20whose%20laws%20will%20be%20imposed%20on%20the%20whole%20nation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDirective%20or%20p%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Erinciple%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Article%2044%20of%20the%20Constitution%20%E2%80%93%20contained%20in%20Part%20IV%2C%20i.e.%20the%20Directive%20Principles%20of%20State%20Policy%20%E2%80%93%20speaks%20of%20a%20UCC%2C%20it%20is%20non-justiciable%20and%20just%20an%20ideal%20objective.%20The%20Directive%20Principles%20(Article%2036%20to%2051)%20are%20violated%20with%20impunity%20and%20often%20by%20the%20state%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20Consider%20just%20Article%2043A%2C%20on%20the%20same%20page%20as%20the%20UCC%2C%20which%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20shall%20take%20steps%2C%20by%20suitable%20legislation%20or%20in%20any%20other%20way%2C%20to%20secure%20the%20participation%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20management%20of%20undertakings%2C%20establishments%20or%20other%20organisations%20engaged%20in%20any%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%20to%20Article%2044%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20had%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fambedkar-favoured-common-civil-code%2Farticle7934565.ece%5C%22%3Ein%20November%201948%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20envisaged%20a%20way%20around%20it%3A%20that%20a%20voluntary%20offer%20may%20be%20the%20way%20of%20bringing%20a%20consensus%20on%20such%20wide-ranging%20practices%3B%20%E2%80%9Ca%20provision%20by%20way%20of%20making%20a%20beginning%20that%20the%20Code%20shall%20apply%20only%20to%20those%20who%20make%20a%20declaration%20that%20they%20are%20prepared%20to%20be%20bound%20by%20it%2C%20so%20that%20in%20the%20initial%20stage%20the%20application%20of%20the%20Code%20may%20be%20purely%20voluntary%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20so%20that%20the%20fear%20which%20my%20friends%20have%20expressed%20here%20will%20be%20altogether%20nullified.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22BJP's%20Clamour%20for%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Driven%20by%20Aim%20of%20Dividing%2C%20Not%20Uniting%2C%20Indians%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjps-clamour-for-uniform-civil-code-driven-by-aim-of-dividing-not-uniting-indians%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Clamour%20for%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Driven%20by%20Aim%20of%20Dividing%2C%20Not%20Uniting%2C%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20there%20already%20is%20a%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201954%2C%20providing%20a%20legal%20umbrella%20for%20inter-religious%2C%20inter-caste%20marriages.%20In%3Cem%3E%20The%20Intimate%20State%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Perveez%20Mody%20has%20studied%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprotections%20(and%20obstructions)%20presented%20by%20the%20law%20to%20those%20who%20transform%20their%20new%20forms%20of%20intimacy%20into%20marriage%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%20A%20true%20progressive%20approach%20would%20be%20to%20expand%20the%20legal%20limits%20of%20how%20%E2%80%98relations%20of%20intimacy%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98family%E2%80%99%20are%20thought%20of%2C%20ideally%20to%20break%20caste%20endogamy%20and%20perhaps%20even%20annihilate%20caste.%20India%20needs%20a%20civil%20code%20that%20is%20uniformly%20progressive%2C%20rather%20than%20uniformly%20regressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20target%20may%20be%20Muslim%20but%20enough%20groups%20which%20are%20parts%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20calculus%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%20tribals%2C%20Goans%2C%20people%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20states%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Parsis%20and%20Christians%20%E2%80%93%20have%20made%20their%20case%20and%20already%20want%20out%20of%20an%20unknown%20uniformity%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20imposed.%20This%20opposition%20will%20spell%20disaster%20for%20the%20BJP%20if%20it%20pursues%20the%20matter%20in%20an%20election%20year.%20Maybe%20that%20explains%20the%20chronology%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20having%20assured%20a%2012-member%20Nagaland%20government%20delegation%2C%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Neiphiu%20Rio%2C%20that%20the%20government%20is%20considering%20exempting%20Christians%20and%20some%20pockets%20of%20tribal%20areas%20from%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20proposed%20contentious%20UCC.%20The%20state%20government%20of%20Nagaland%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmorungexpress.com%2Fcentre-considering-exemption-of-christians-tribal-areas-from-ucc-purview-state-govt%5C%22%3Eactually%20said%20so%20in%20an%20official%20press%20release%20on%20July%207%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%2C%20Schedule%20Six%2C%20the%20box%20for%20exceptions%20is%20already%20being%20carved%20up.%20Article%20371%20(A%20to%20J)%20mandates%20exceptions%20for%20regions%20and%20persons.%20So%2C%20once%20it%20is%20decided%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98uniform%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20will%20be%20exempted%20and%20who%20won%E2%80%99t%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMechanics%20of%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Commission%20is%20being%20relied%20upon%20as%20the%20nodal%20body%20to%20work%20on%20the%20UCC%20to%20prepare%20something%20the%20BJP%20wants.%20But%20the%20Law%20Commission%20has%20already%20said%20clearly%20in%20para%201.15%20of%20a%20detailed%20report%20in%202018%20that%20a%20UCC%20was%20%E2%80%9Cneither%20necessary%20nor%20desirable%E2%80%9D.%20To%20cite%20the%20full%20sentence%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20Commission%20has%20therefore%20dealt%20with%20laws%20that%20are%20discriminatory%20rather%20than%20providing%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20which%20is%20neither%20necessary%20nor%20desirable%20at%20this%20stage.%20Most%20countries%20are%20now%20moving%20towards%20recognition%20of%20difference%2C%20and%20the%20mere%20existence%20of%20difference%20does%20not%20imply%20discrimination%2C%20but%20is%20indicative%20of%20a%20robust%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%20That%20is%20completely%20at%20variance%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98one%20size%20fits%20all%E2%80%99%20being%20sought%20by%20a%20majoritarian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20the%20BJP%20government%20cares%20for%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission%20is%20clear%20from%20at%20least%20two%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20it%20is%20disregarding%20the%20recommendations%20of%20its%20own%20appointees%20in%20the%2021st%20Law%20Commission%20from%202018%20saying%20the%20UCC%20is%20a%20no%20go%20and%20personal%20laws%20should%20just%20be%20urged%20to%20evolve%20out%20of%20bad%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20this%20government%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20appoint%20members%20to%20the%2022nd%C2%A0Law%20Commission%20for%20years.%20The%2022%3Csup%3End%3C%2Fsup%3E%20Law%20Commission%20was%20a%20ghost%20commission%20for%20nearly%20all%20of%20its%20three-year%20term.%20Notified%20on%20February%2021%2C%202020%2C%20it%20was%20kept%20vacant%20for%20two%20years%20and%20nine%20months%20of%20its%20three-year%20term.%20A%20chairperson%2C%20Justice%C2%A0Rituraj%20Awasthi%C2%A0(retd)%2C%20finally%20assumed%20office%20on%C2%A0November%209%2C%202022.%20Its%20term%20has%20now%20been%20extended%20till%20August%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%2021st%20Law%20Commission%20put%20forth%20its%20questionnaire%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20in%20November%202016%2C%20it%20received%20over%2075%2C378%20responses.%20This%20time%2C%20the%2022nd%C2%A0Law%20Commission%20has%20to%20deal%20with%2046%20lakh%20responses.%20What%20is%20the%20process%20for%20sifting%20through%20this%3F%20What%20is%20the%20process%20of%20reinventing%20the%20UCC%20wheel%3F%20Nothing%20is%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProgressive%20civil%20code%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20group%20comprising%20activist%20Bezwada%20Wilson%2C%20lawyer%20Dushyant%2C%20actor%20Gul%20Panag%2C%20academic%20and%20author%20Mukul%20Kesavan%2C%20author%20Nilanjana%20Roy%2C%20scholar%20S.%20Irfan%20Habib%2C%20Major%20General%20S.%20Vombetkere%20(retd)%20and%20musician%20T.M.%20Krishna%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fgovernment%2Funiform-civil-code-draft-law-commission%2Famp%5C%22%3Epresented%20a%20proposal%20of%20a%20model%20progressive%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Justice%20B.S.%20Chauhan%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission.%20They%20conceived%20of%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20HUF%2C%20gender-neutral%20marriage%20and%20inheritance%20laws%2C%20which%20would%20entitle%20all%20children%20%E2%80%93%20biological%2C%20adopted%2C%20surrogate%2C%20%E2%80%98legitimate%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98illegitimate%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20to%20inherit%20property.%20In%20a%20supporting%20letter%2C%20former%20attorney%20general%20Soli%20J.%20Sorabjee%2C%20who%20forwarded%20the%20draft%20code%20to%20Justice%20Chauhan%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20join%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20ensure%20that%20any%20step%20ahead%20to%20bring%20everyone%20on%20the%20same%20page%20must%20be%20progressive%20and%20enlightened.%E2%80%9D%20Sorabjee%20added%20that%20the%20Law%20Commissions%20recommendations%20on%20a%20UCC%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cfar-sighted%20and%20progressive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20root%20of%20the%20problem%20is%20how%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20view%20diversity.%20A%20good%20talking%20point%20for%20foreign%20trips%2C%20it%20came%20up%20in%20Paris%20too%20on%20Thursday.%20But%20it%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Caffront%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20unity%E2%80%9D%20for%20domestic%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20many%20species%20of%20flora%20and%20fauna%20in%20the%20Amazon%20forest%2C%20the%20diversity%20of%20India%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Efact%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20inclusiveness%20or%20wanting%20a%20healthy%20and%20plural%20pastiche%20is%20an%20%3Cem%3Eact%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20speaks%20to%20what%20a%20society%20wants%20to%20do%20with%20its%20diversity.%20As%20a%20modern%20democracy%20in%201950%2C%20India%20was%20anxious%20to%20embrace%20it.%20The%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20for%20India%2075%20years%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22BJP%20Equates%20UCC%20With%20Gender%20Justice.%20But%20Can%20It%20End%20Discrimination%20In-Built%20in%20Personal%20Laws%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fbjp-ucc-with-gender-justice-discrimination-personal-laws%5C%22%3EBJP%20Equates%20UCC%20With%20Gender%20Justice.%20But%20Can%20It%20End%20Discrimination%20In-Built%20in%20Personal%20Laws%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20wanting%20a%20UCC%20is%20the%20obsession%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98U%E2%80%99.%202023%20calls%20for%20a%20Progressive%20or%20a%20P%2C%20a%20PCC.%20But%20a%20majoritarian%20BJP%20is%20keen%20on%20just%20clinging%20onto%20anything%20it%20hopes%20will%20fire%20its%20base.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20purpose%20is%20to%20indulge%20in%20performative%20exclusion%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20to%20tell%20its%20base%20that%20it%20has%20obliterated%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20would%20also%20like%20to%20say%20it%20has%20been%20able%20to%20impose%20the%20%E2%80%98uniformity%E2%80%99%20of%20Hindu%20Law%20but%20there%20is%20no%20one%20Hindu%20law%20which%20will%20be%20acceptable%20across%20the%20country%20to%20all%20Hindus%20and%20non-Hindus%20(i.e.%2C%20not%20just%20Muslims%20but%20Christians%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Tribals%2C%20Sikhs%20etc.)%20Any%20exercise%20that%20dives%20into%20the%20details%2C%20even%20if%20a%20stitched-up%20quickie%20Code%2C%20will%20be%20a%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20box%2C%20full%20of%20elements%20unacceptable%20to%20everyone%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%20the%20UCC%20as%20a%20concrete%20proposal%20is%20AWOL.%20Try%20persuading%20any%20Hindu%20family%20in%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20constituency%20in%20UP%20that%20it%20is%20ok%20to%20marry%20a%20%3Cem%3Emama%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20first-cousin.%20And%20try%20persuading%20a%20Hindu%20family%20in%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20stop%20doing%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689497235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F09092822%2FIMG_1682.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-knows-an-actual-ucc-will-be-an-electoral-disaster-for-him%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Who%20will%20it%20be%20uniform%20for%3F%20The%20chronology%20is%20clear%20as%20Hindus%20would%20want%20out%20too.%20The%20BJP%20realises%20this%20and%20hence%2C%20there%20is%20no%20UCC%20draft%20being%20made%20available%2C%20just%20hot%20air.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A89%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-knows-an-actual-ucc-will-be-an-electoral-disaster-for-him%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22File%20ITR%20soon%20as%20govt%20not%20contemplating%20deadline%20extension%3A%20Revenue%20secy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689496568000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-09%2F13%2Ffull%2F1631477818-5867.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ffile-itr-at-earliest-as-govt-no