on-codified%20nature%20of%20Muslim%20personal%20law%20makes%20it%20prone%20to%20misinterpretation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20absence%20of%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20has%20perpetuated%20inequalities%20and%20inconsistencies%20in%20our%20diverse%20nation.%20It%20hinders%20progress%20towards%20social%20harmony%2C%20economic%20growth%2C%20and%20gender%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20absence%20of%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20has%20perpetuated%20inequalities%20and%20inconsistencies%20in%20our%20diverse%20nation.%20It%20hinders%20progress%20towards%20social%20harmony%2C%20economic%20growth%2C%20and%20gender%20justice.%20In%20India%2C%20the%20Muslim%20community%20follows%20Muslim%20personal%20law%2C%20which%20being%20non-codified%2C%20is%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3Wdz8ISx6t%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F3Wdz8ISx6t%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NCW%20(%40NCWIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNCWIndia%2Fstatus%2F1680169679338487808%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20the%20Muslim%20community%20follows%20Muslim%20personal%20law%2C%20which%20being%20non-codified%2C%20is%20prone%20to%20misinterpretation%20and%20poses%20challenges%20for%20Muslim%20women.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20address%20these%20issues%20for%20a%20more%20equitable%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deliberation%20came%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission%20seeking%20fresh%20inputs%20last%20month%20on%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20commission%20extended%20the%20deadline%20for%20submission%20of%20views%20to%20July%2028.%20Earlier%20it%20had%20set%20July%2014%20as%20the%20deadline%20to%20send%20inputs%20on%20the%20contentious%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20Commission%20said%20that%20it%20had%20received%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fas-deadline-nears-law-commission-receives-46-lakh-responses-on-uniform-civil-code%5C%22%3E46%20lakh%20responses%20on%20its%20notice.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCW%20chairperson%20Rekha%20Sharma%20said%20that%20there%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20codified%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20pursuit%20of%20equality%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20reflect%3A%20if%20a%20law%20cannot%20serve%20the%20rights%20of%20Hindu%2C%20Christian%2C%20Sikh%2C%20and%20Buddhist%20women%2C%20can%20we%20truly%20say%20it%20is%20just%20for%20Muslim%20women%3F%20The%20need%20for%20codified%20laws%20is%20urgent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20NCW%20Chairperson%20during%20Final%20consultation%20on%20Rights%20of%20Muslim%20Women%20-Reviewing%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsharmarekha%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40sharmarekha%3C%2Fa%3E%20said-%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20pursuit%20of%20equality%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20reflect%3A%20if%20a%20law%20cannot%20serve%20the%20rights%20of%20Hindu%2C%20Christian%2C%20Sikh%2C%20and%20Buddhist%20women%2C%20can%20we%20truly%20say%20it%20is%20just%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FY4HrakNkTk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FY4HrakNkTk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NCW%20(%40NCWIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNCWIndia%2Fstatus%2F1680116351019671553%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20work%20towards%20a%20legal%20framework%20that%20ensures%20equal%20rights%20for%20all%2C%20regardless%20of%20religion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deliberations%20on%20Saturday%20saw%20the%20participation%20of%20key%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20representatives%20from%20high%20courts%2C%20Vice%20Chancellors%20of%20law%20universities%2C%20legal%20luminaries%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20reported%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ER.%20Venkataramani%2C%20the%20Attorney-General%20of%20India%2C%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20reforming%20and%20strengthening%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Venkataramani)%20emphasised%20the%20following%20points%3Aequal%20regard%20for%20men%20and%20women%2C%20equal%20status%20for%20men%20and%20women%2C%20equality%20of%20processes%20ensuring%20dignity%20in%20entering%20and%20exiting%20marital%20relationships%20irrespective%20of%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20ANI%20reported%2C%20quoting%20an%20NCW%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCW%20also%20said%20that%20the%20deliberations%20also%20included%20consultations%20on%20reforming%20divorce%20as%20a%20judicial%20process%2C%20with%20exception%20to%20divorce%20through%20mutual%20consent%2C%20and%20the%20need%20to%20reform%20inheritance%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20notification%20last%20month%20came%20despite%20the%2021st%20commission%20suggesting%20in%202018%20that%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20%E2%80%9Cis%20neither%20necessary%20nor%20desirable%20at%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20more%20than%20three%20years%20have%20lapsed%20from%20the%20date%20of%20issuance%20of%20the%20said%20consultation%20paper%2C%20bearing%20in%20mind%20the%20relevance%20and%20importance%20of%20the%20subject%20and%20also%20the%20various%20court%20orders%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20the%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%20considered%20it%20expedient%20to%20deliberate%20afresh%20over%20the%20subject%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20commission%E2%80