539231233%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20aims%20to%20establish%20a%20framework%20that%20encourages%20the%20utilisation%20of%20local%20currencies%2C%20specifically%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20(INR)%20and%20the%20UAE%20Dirham%20(AED)%2C%20for%20cross-border%20transactions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20MoU%20focuses%20on%20cooperation%20for%20interlinking%20their%20payment%20and%20messaging%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20primary%20objective%20of%20the%20MoU%20on%20establishing%20a%20framework%20for%20the%20use%20of%20local%20currencies%20is%20to%20implement%20a%20Local%20Currency%20Settlement%20System%20(LCSS)%20that%20promotes%20bilateral%20use%20of%20the%20INR%20and%20AED%20for%20transactions%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20emphasised%20that%20the%20agreement%20for%20trade%20settlement%20in%20the%20currencies%20of%20both%20nations%20exemplifies%20the%20robust%20economic%20cooperation%20and%20mutual%20trust%20shared%20by%20India%20and%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThree%20transformative%20MoUs%20were%20exchanged%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%EF%B8%8F%E2%83%A3%20MoU%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRBI%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RBI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26amp%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcentralbankuae%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40centralbankuae%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20framework%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20local%20currencies%20(INR%20%E2%80%93%20AED)%20for%20cross-border%20transactions%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2%EF%B8%8F%E2%83%A3%20MoU%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%