E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20same%20report%20he%20is%20quoted%20as%20having%20said%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CMiya%20traders%20are%20charging%20high%20prices%20for%20vegetables%20from%20Assamese%20people%20in%20Guwahati%2C%20while%20the%20price%20of%20vegetables%20is%20lesser%20in%20the%20villages.%20If%20Assamese%20seller%20had%20been%20selling%20vegetables%20today%2C%20they%20would%20never%20have%20charged%20more%20from%20their%20fellow%20Assamese.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanta%20also%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20would%20personally%20get%20vegetable%20markets%20under%20flyovers%20vacated%2C%20so%20that%20%E2%80%9CAssamese%20boys%E2%80%9D%20could%20get%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20At%20present%2C%20most%20of%20the%20people%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20under%20the%20flyovers%20of%20Guwahati%20are%20Muslims%20from%20the%20Miya%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanta%20also%20appeared%20to%20blame%20Muslim%20drivers%20of%20public%20transport%20for%20celebrating%20Eid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20have%20seen%20how%20the%20movement%20of%20buses%20in%20Guwahati%20city%20reduces%20during%20Eid.%20Less%20crowds%20are%20seen.%20Because%20most%20of%20the%20bus%20and%20cab%20drivers%20are%20from%20the%20Miyan%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20All%20India%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20president%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Badruddin%20Ajmal%20had%20said%20that%20Assam%20is%20incomplete%20without%20the%20Miya%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanta%20responded%2C%20saying%20that%20Ajmal%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinsulted%20the%20Assamese%20community%E2%80%9D%20by%20making%20such%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20two%20days%20after%20it%20was%20inaugurated%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98Miya%20Museum%E2%80%99%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Goalpara%20district%20was%20sealed%20and%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20museum%20was%20taken%20into%20custody.%20The%20museum%20was%20set%20up%20by%20Mohor%20Ali%2C%20pr