turing%20Ratlami%20sev.%20The%20Sakhlecha%20family%20of%20Ratlam%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20commercial%20manufacturers%20of%20the%20sev.%20In%20the%20early%201900s%2C%20the%20first%20shop%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Late%20Shantilal%20Sakhlecha%20with%20his%20father%20Late%20Kesarmal%20Sakhlecha.%20Today%2C%20several%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252694%2Fswati-snacks-minakshi-jhaveri-iconic-eatery-india-inspiring-single-mother-success-stories-authentic-homemade-food-chaat-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnack%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20manufacture%20the%20snack%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Indore%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sev%20was%20awarded%20the%20Geographical%20Indication%20Tag%20(GI)%20in%202014-15.%20As%20per%20the%20application%20filed%20for%20the%20GI%20indicator%2C%20the%20applicants%20%E2%80%94%20Ratlam%20Sev%20Evam%20Namkeen%20Mandal%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20production%20of%20the%20Ratlami%20sev%20had%20been%20going%20on%20for%20at%20least%20200%20years%20at%20the%20household%20level%2C%20but%20from%20the%20first%20decade%20of%20the%20last%20century%2C%20it%20has%20been%20commercially%20produced%20and%20marketed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20an%20intrinsic%20part%20of%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20the%20snack%20today%20has%20many%20contenders%20staking%20their%20claim%20to%20its%20manufacturing.%20A%20long-standing%20legal%20battle%20threatens%20to%20evict%20members%20of%20the%20community%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20large%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304840%2Fengineer-builds-online-marketplace-for-indian-mothers-to-sell-homemade-food-momskart%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Enamkeen%20%3C%2Fem%3Emanufacturers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20as%20the%20former%E2%80%99s%20ancestors%20are%20the%20original%20creators%20of%20the%20